Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.36,0:00:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the Still of the Night - The Five Satins
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.36,0:00:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? In the still of the night ?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.74,0:00:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? I held you ?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.90,0:00:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? Held you tight ?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.57,0:00:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? 'Cause I love ?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.24,0:00:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? Love you so ?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.74,0:00:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? Promise I'll never ?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.82,0:00:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? Let you go ?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.99,0:00:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? In the still of the night ?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.95,0:01:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? In the still of the night ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.78,0:01:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? I remember ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.99,0:01:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? That night in May ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.32,0:01:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? The stars were bright above ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.90,0:01:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? I'll hope and I'll pray ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.03,0:01:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? To keep Your precious love... ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.82,0:01:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我年轻的时候  以为刷房子真就是刷房子\NWhen I was young, I thought house painters painted houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.40,0:01:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我懂什么\NWhat did I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.40,0:01:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当时是个工人\NI was a working guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.78,0:01:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,南费城的卡车司机107号地方工会的工会代表\NA business agent for Teamster Local 107 out of South Philly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.78,0:01:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千百个工人中的一员\NOne of a thousand working stiffs...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.86,0:01:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到我不再是了\Nuntil I wasn't no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.65,0:02:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后\NAnd then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.86,0:02:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我开始刷房子\NI started painting houses...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.61,0:02:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亲自\Nmyself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们女儿的婚礼\N格蕾丝・安妮・巴法利诺\N嫁给\N罗伯特・里特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.90,0:02:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这件事情上\NIn this particular matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.28,0:02:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是围绕着婚礼的\Nthe whole thing was built around the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.03,0:02:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比尔・巴法利诺的女儿在底特律结婚\NBill Bufalino's daughter was getting married in Detroit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.45,0:02:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比尔是卡车司机工会的律师  但更重要的是\NBill was a Teamster lawyer, but more important,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.61,0:02:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是罗素・巴法利诺的表亲\Nhe was Russell Bufalino's cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.90,0:02:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗素不想坐飞机\NNow, Russell didn't want to fly,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.32,0:02:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我打算开车送他去参加婚礼\Nso I was gonna drive him to the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想顺路处理一些生意上的事情\NHe wanted to take care of some business along the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.53,0:02:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对罗素而言  这就意味着一件事\Nwhich in Russell's case meant only one thing:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.24,0:02:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钱  收钱\NMoney... collecting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:02:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们开车去的\NSo we'd drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他和他老婆凯丽  以及我和我老婆艾琳\NHim and his wife Carrie and me and my wife Irene.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喊她琳妮\NOr I call her Reenie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想着我们走费城外的476号公路\NI figured we would take 476 out of Philly,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.90,0:03:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们到匹兹顿接上罗素\Nand then we go up to Pittston and pick up Russ,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.40,0:03:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们一般都是这么走的\Nwhich is usually how we did it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.03,0:03:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后沿80号州际公路西段开过宾州\Nand then Interstate 80 West through the rest of Pennsylvania,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.15,0:03:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们横穿俄亥俄州到托莱多\Nand then we'd go across Ohio, all the way to Toledo,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接着我们沿着75号公路北上底特律\Nand then we would go 75 North to Detroit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总共要花三天\NIt was gonna take about three days
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.15,0:03:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算上所有谈生意以及抽烟的时间\Nwith all the business breaks and cigarette stops,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.49,0:03:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为罗素不允许任何人在车里面抽烟\Nsince Russell didn't allow nobody to smoke in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.74,0:03:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说蓝眼睛吉米和迈尔・兰斯基\NHe says Jimmy Blue Eyes and Meyer Lansky
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.70,0:03:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说服他戒了烟\Nconvinced him to stop smoking
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当时他们从自己在古巴的赌场里被赶了出去\Nwhen they were getting kicked out of their casinos in Cuba
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还被卡斯特罗开枪打了\Nand getting shot at by Castro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.90,0:03:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也说不清楚  也许是那种\NI don't know. It might have been one of those,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"上帝啊如果我活着度过这一劫\N"Please-God-if-I-ever-get-out- of-this-fucking-thing-alive-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.78,0:03:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就再也不抽烟了"的情况\NI'll-never-smoke-again things too."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.24,0:03:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我知道从卡斯特罗那件事开始\NBut I do know that from Castro on,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗素就再也不许别人在车里抽烟了\NRuss wouldn't allow nobody to smoke in his car,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:03:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就连凯丽也不行\Nnot even Carrie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.86,0:04:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刷房子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能尽快停车吗\NCan we stop soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们刚上车两分钟  亲爱的\NWe're only in the car two minutes, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至还没上公路呢\NWe're not even near the highway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  罗素  但你不喜欢在公路上停车\NI know, Russell. But you don't like to stop on the highway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.99,0:04:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不能这么说\NWell, it's not that so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.24,0:04:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他们不允许你在公路上停车\NThey don't let you stop on the highway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  那我们就在车里抽吧\NOkay, so then we'll smoke in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的白内障怎么办\NAnd what about my cataracts?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.86,0:04:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会开窗的\NI'll crack the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯丽  我发过誓的  记得吗\NCarrie, I made a vow. Remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.36,0:04:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记得我发过誓吗  凯丽\NRemember I made a vow, Carrie?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.24,0:04:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  这下我不能在...\NYeah, now I can't smoke on...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行吧  这下我不能抽烟了\NAll right, and now I can't smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.78,0:05:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看见我们到哪了吗\NSee where we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是...\NIs... Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太巧了吧\NWhat are those odds?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德士古石油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出什么问题了  小子\NWhat's the problem, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.11,0:06:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道  感觉车坏了\NI don't... I don't know. It sounds funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,车停了  再启动  就没动力了\NIt stops, it starts, it loses power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.32,0:06:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看能不能给你搭把手\NLet me see if I can give you a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.24,0:06:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看  检查一下这些塞子\NLet me see. Check all these plugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.90,0:06:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,火花塞没问题\NSpark plugs are okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分电盘盖也没问题\NThe distributor cap's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.61,0:06:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\NGood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.86,0:06:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是这个...出问题了\NIt's gotta be something with... with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.61,0:06:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,定时链\NTiming chain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.36,0:07:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么回事  这上面有个塞子\NThis is what this is. There's a cap on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个塞子松了  不应该松的\NThis cap is loose. It ain't supposed to be loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.53,0:07:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以这意味着它们已经老化了\NSo that means they're getting worn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.45,0:07:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得...\NYou just gotta...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,试试  拧紧它\NTry that now. Tighten it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会开车  但不会修车\NI can drive 'em. I can't fix 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.32,0:07:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以重新上路了  小子\NYou're back in business, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢了\NThanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.61,0:07:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我怎么回报你呢  -不用\N- I owe you anything? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.20,0:07:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不用回报我\NNo, you don't owe me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢了\NThanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.40,0:07:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我叫弗兰克  -你好  弗兰克\N- Frank. - Hey, Frank. How ya doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.82,0:07:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么\NWhat's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.36,0:07:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪里人\NWhere you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-费城  -你是费城人啊\N- Philly. - Oh, you're from Philly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.32,0:07:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在费城你一般去哪玩\NWhere you hang out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,0:07:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡拉汉\NCallahan's.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滚球俱乐部\NBocce Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.44,0:07:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那是个酒吧  不是玩滚球的俱乐部\NBut it's a bar, it's not a bocce club.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.86,0:07:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛  你玩滚球吗\NOh, yeah. You play bocce?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.82,0:07:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不玩\NNah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.03,0:08:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  弗兰克  把那玩意修好\NAll right, Frankie... get that fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.99,0:08:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为它肯定还会掉链子的  我告诉你\NBecause it'll go again on you, I'm telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.82,0:08:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-谢谢  -好了\N- Thank you. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.49,0:08:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会去修的  再次感谢\NI will. Thanks again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.52,0:08:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你好运  小兄弟\NGood luck, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为他是加油站老板\NI mean, I thought maybe he owned the gas station.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他一定是个老板  看得出来\N'Cause he owned something, you could tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果发现整条路都是他的\NYeah, it turns out he owned the whole road.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Hear You Knockin' - Smiley Lewis
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? You went away and left me long time ago ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛排和猪排
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.00,0:08:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,友好酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? And now you're knocking on my door ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这只吗\NThis one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.81,0:08:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? I hear you knocking ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.99,0:08:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敬礼  干了  朋友们\NSalute! Drink up, fellas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.86,0:08:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝保佑\NGod bless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.24,0:08:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走着  走着  今天一起赚点钱\NLet's go. Let's go. Let's make some money today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.45,0:08:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可是个酒吧\NIt's a bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向你老婆问好\NSay hello to your wife, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有个赚钱的法子  推销那些后腿肉\NI got a way you can earn, to push those hindquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.90,0:08:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里有个人  他会为此出大价钱的\NThere's a guy in here, he'll pay a lot of money for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.57,0:09:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  我们先干了再谈生意\NCome on, let's shoot this first and then we'll talk business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.07,0:09:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在酒吧的另一头  十二点钟方向...\NAt the other end of the bar, at twelve o'clock...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.03,0:09:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看见他了吗  有点秃的那个\NYou see him? He's got a rescinding hairline.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错  他能让你赚大钱\NYeah, you'll make a lot of money with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看见他了吗  瘦剃刀  他是这地方的老板\NSee him there? Skinny Razor. He owns the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剃刀\NRazor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.45,0:09:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他放高利贷  还在酒吧开了个赌注站\NHe shylocks and runs a little book out of the joint.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他挺能耐的  人脉很广\NHe's got a lot of good action, good connections.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他叫剃刀  -是的  他曾经在肉店工作\N- Razor's his name? - Yeah, he used to work at a butcher shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我朋友爱尔兰人弗兰克在这里\NMy friend Frank Irish is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.41,0:09:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和你说过的那个\NThe one I told you about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.24,0:09:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-开卡车的  -对  运后腿肉\N- Oh, the truck. - Yeah, hindquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是弗兰克・希兰\NFrank Sheeran.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.28,0:09:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢牛排吗\NYou like steak?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.53,0:09:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢\NI do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.70,0:09:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我送牛排\NI deliver steak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.86,0:09:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗\NDo ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.86,0:09:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上好的牛排\NGood steak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.78,0:09:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以给你送牛排\NI could deliver you steak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.82,0:09:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-可以吗  -可以\N- Could ya? - I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,价格也公道  最低价\NGood price too. The best.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我们晚点再聊  -好的\N- We'll talk later. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:09:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢了  瘦子\NThanks, Skinny.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.28,0:10:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外面冷死了\NIt's freezing out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.72,0:10:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不介意\NI don't mind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.03,0:10:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不行  我怕冷\NNot me. I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.74,0:10:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮我个忙  你出去的时候...\NHey, do me a favor. When you go outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮我把封条装上\Nput the seal on for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.36,0:10:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好吧  反正我得出去  -我欠你个人情\N- All right. I gotta go out anyway. - I owe you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.65,0:10:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? You'd better go back to your used-to-be ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? Because your love's no good to me ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.36,0:10:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? I hear you knocking ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.99,0:10:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,友好酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? But you can't come in ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? I hear you knocking ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? Go back where you've been ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? They call, they call me the fat man ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.82,0:11:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? 'Cause I weigh two hundred pounds... ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.65,0:11:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,25块  A级后腿肉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给  弗兰克\NThere you go, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-下次见  -好的  托尼  谢了\N- See you next time. - All right, Tony. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.78,0:11:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好多了  弗兰克\NMuch better, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.45,0:11:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不碰特选级  只运极佳级\NI don't go near Choice. I only do Prime. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.45,0:11:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美国牛肉分级制度中\N极佳级和特选级\N分别为最好的前两个等级
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.74,0:11:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下周二能再给我搞一些来吗\NCan I get some more for next Tuesday?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想要多少\NHow many you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.99,0:11:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少五块\NAt least five.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的  给你五块\NOkay. Five, you got.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-阿门  -阿门\N- Amen. - Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.53,0:11:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿门\NAmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这他妈是怎么回事\NWhat the fuck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.36,0:12:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托尼  我不...\NTony, I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.86,0:12:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这他妈是怎么回事  弗兰克\NWhat the fuck is this, Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\NI don't... I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.32,0:12:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说...\NI mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,车不是我装的\NI don't load the truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.53,0:12:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是装车的人装的车\NThe loaders are supposed to load the truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.15,0:12:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许他们没干好自己的活儿  我不知道\NMaybe they didn't do their work. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,0:12:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没意识到车变轻了吗\NYou didn't realize you were driving a light horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.95,0:12:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有  我只是...\NNo. I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.89,0:12:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没意识到  感觉挺正常的\NNothing. It felt fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.03,0:12:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  弗兰克  拜托\NOh, come on, Frank. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说的是真的  我...\NI'm telling you. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.11,0:12:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千真万确  我真不知道是怎么回事\NGod's truth. I just don't know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.28,0:12:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道  也许是...\NI don't know. Maybe some...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.65,0:12:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-车是空的  -我知道\N- It's empty. - I know it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\NI know it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们看什么看  回去工作\NWhat are you guys looking at? Go back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有人\NAll of youse!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么和老板交待\NWhat am I gonna tell the boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说了我真不知道是怎么回事\NWell, I'm telling you that I don't know what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别问我  因为我...\NJust don't look at me 'cause I, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.99,0:12:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我还能去问谁\NWell, who else can I look at?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.28,0:12:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这件事可不能怪在我头上  弗兰克\NThis is not gonna be on me, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:12:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我都说了  -也怪不到我头上\N- I'm telling you right now. - Not gonna be on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.03,0:12:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是开车的  别的什么都没干\NI just drive the truck. That's all I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.45,0:13:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  弗兰克・希兰  是叫这个吗\NOkay, Frank Sheeran. Am I saying that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.65,0:13:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,律师\N威廉・E・巴法利诺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.24,0:13:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  就是这名字\NYeah, you said right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根据合同  这得感谢吉米・霍法\NUnder the contract, thanks to Jimmy Hoffa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.11,0:13:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理层只能在有非常具体的指控时才能开除司机\Nmanagement can only fire a driver on very specific charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你上班迟到过吗  -没有\N- So, you ever show up late? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.82,0:13:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-有任何交通违规吗  -没有\N- Do you have any moving violations? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.53,0:13:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你在工作期间喝酒吗  -不喝\N- Do you drink on the job? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.32,0:13:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打过人吗\NYou ever hit anybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-在工作期间吗  -对\N- On the job? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.45,0:13:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-那没有  -好的\N- No. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偷窃不算吗\NWhat about stealing, that ain't grounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛\NWell...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.90,0:13:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们能证明吗\Ncan they prove it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.11,0:13:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该不能\NI don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.15,0:13:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就没什么好担心的了\NAll right then, we don't have nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.15,0:13:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他们能证明\NIf they can prove it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.11,0:13:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们也只是想让你供出其他同伙的名字\Nthey're just gonna want names from you. Accomplices.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.74,0:13:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已  你交代几个名字就能回家了\NThat's all. You give them a couple of names, you go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.20,0:13:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还能保住你的工作\NKeep your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得怎么样\NWhat do you think about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.40,0:13:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你会交代名字吗  -不\N- Would you give them names? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.86,0:13:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有名字\NNo names.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.28,0:13:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吧  我并不...\NYou know, I don't, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.03,0:13:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我并不关心你到底做没做\NI don't care whether you did it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.20,0:13:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说没有区别\NThat makes no difference to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:14:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我知道  -我是来帮你辩护的  对吧\N- Yeah, I know. - I'm here to defend you. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  你想知道我到底做没做吗\NWhat, you want to know if I did it or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛\NWell...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.90,0:14:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样我都会替你辩护\NI'm gonna defend you either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.15,0:14:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  只是...\NYeah, all right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.07,0:14:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没偷他们东西时可是勤勤恳恳工作的\NI, I work hard for them when I ain't stealing from 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法官大人  如果这是是非对错的问题\NYour Honor, if this was about right or wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.53,0:14:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公司应该早就开除希兰先生了\Nthe company would have sought Mr. Sheeran's dismissal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.11,0:14:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可他们没有\NThey didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们指控希兰先生\NThey only accused Mr. Sheeran
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.11,0:14:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是因为公司希望他能指认同伙\Nbecause the company hoped he could name conspirators,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而他没法指认  因为并不存在什么同伙\Nwhich he couldn't do because they don't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.82,0:14:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不存在同伙是因为他并没有偷东西\NThey don't exist because he didn't steal anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.61,0:14:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他没偷东西是因为他是个模范员工\NHe didn't steal anything because he's an exemplary employee,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.28,0:14:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工作八年都没请过一天病假\Nwho in eight years has never taken a day of sick leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他唯一违反过的只有他自己工会的规矩\NThe only rule he ever broke is his own union's,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在冷死人的大冬天  帮其他人把半扇半扇的牛肉\Nby helping others carry sides of beef from his truck
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从他的卡车上搬进他们的冷藏库里\Nto their refrigerators in the dead of winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.32,0:14:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全体起立\NAll rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在开庭\NCourt is in session.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.78,0:15:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要驳回此案并给予警告\NI'm dismissing this case with a warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.99,0:15:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的  法官大人\NYes, Your Honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.99,0:15:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是警告你  希兰先生\NNo, no, not you, Mr. Sheeran.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.95,0:15:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们下次要是再把工人告上法庭\NYou bring another working man before this court
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.45,0:15:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有证据而只有威胁\Nwith threats instead of evidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.15,0:15:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信我  你们会后悔的\Nbelieve me, you'll be sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.82,0:15:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我持有这家公司的股份  我一定赶紧卖了\NIf I owned stock in this company, I would sell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.57,0:15:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道他怎么做到的  我也不会问\NI don't know how he did it, and I ain't gonna ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.95,0:15:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只知道比尔・巴法利诺帮我摆脱了一件\NAll I know is that Bill Bufalino got me out of
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.99,0:15:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我原本绝无可能脱身的案子\Na case where I should never have gotten away with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗马别墅餐厅酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.95,0:15:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本该彻底败诉的\NI should've been down for the count.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.45,0:15:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们会感谢你今天的所作所为  弗兰克\NPeople are gonna appreciate what you did today, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.95,0:15:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们有家人  有孩子\NYou know, they got families, they got kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们需要这些工作\NThey need those jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而  我们却在外庆祝\NInstead, we went out celebrating...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.07,0:15:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗素\NRussell!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.78,0:15:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我则就此走上了\N...and I met what was gonna turn out to be
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.49,0:15:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,余生的道路\Nthe rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就觉得刚进来的人是你\NYou know, I thought that was you walking in outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.61,0:15:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然了  这可是我们的地盘\NYeah, yeah, you know, this is our place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.45,0:15:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我给你介绍个叫弗兰克的新人吧\NCan I introduce you to this new guy Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.82,0:15:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然  好的\NYeah, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗兰克  来见见我的表兄罗素・巴法利诺\NFrank, I want you to meet my cousin Russell Bufalino.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.78,0:15:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你好啊  -你好  幸会\N- How are ya? - Hi, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.40,0:15:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几个月前你帮我修过我的卡车\NYou helped me with my truck a couple of months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.65,0:15:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错  想起来了  定时链坏了\NOh, yeah, yeah, that's right. The timing chain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.99,0:16:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-对  -你找人修了吗\N- Yeah. - Did you get it fixed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.49,0:16:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我第二天就找人修了  -好样的\N- I fixed it the next day, yeah. - Attaboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-再次感谢你  -不客气\N- Thanks again. - Oh, you're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.70,0:16:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的荣幸  你修好了就好\NMy pleasure. I'm glad you fixed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最好注意点\NYou better watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里有很多不好惹的家伙  他跟你说了吗\NThere's a lot of tough guys around here. Did he tell ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你并不怕不好惹的家伙  是吧\NYou're not afraid of tough guys, are ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是  回见\NI didn't think so. I'll see you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.24,0:16:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好的  -谢了  罗素\N- Okay. - Thanks, Russell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.86,0:16:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你表兄之前帮了我大忙\NYour cousin saved my ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.86,0:16:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然我可能会损失一整车的货\NI could've lost the whole load.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.36,0:16:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  他非常了解卡车\NYeah, yeah. Well, he knows everything about trucks, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.11,0:16:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在汽水公司干过很长时间\NYeah, he worked at Canada Dry for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.95,0:16:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-维托  你好吗  -幸会\N- Vito, how are you? - Pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们去坐卡座吧\NI think, uh... Let's take the booth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.03,0:16:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  你会喜欢这里的\NCome on. You're gonna love this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.45,0:16:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许我当时还不知道罗素・巴法利诺是谁\NMaybe I didn't know who Russell Bufalino was back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.65,0:16:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我在报纸上看过无数照片和报道\Nbut I'd seen enough pictures and stories in the newspapers
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.49,0:16:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,足以知道当时跟他一起吃饭的是安吉洛・布鲁诺\Nto know he was eatin' with Angelo Bruno.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺当时刚成为\NI mean, Bruno, he... he was just made
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.28,0:16:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,费城的新任老大\Nthe new boss of Philadelphia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.24,0:16:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从费城到大西洋城的一切都由他负责\NHe took care of everything from Philadelphia to Atlantic City.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这点我是知道的\NThat, I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:17:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安吉洛・布鲁诺\N1980年在自家门外的自家车里\N头部中枪而亡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.99,0:17:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我当时只需知道这些\NAnd that was all I had to know
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.95,0:17:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能知道罗素・巴法利诺\Nto know that Russell Bufalino
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.70,0:17:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝不是汽水公司的卡车维修工\Nwas no truck mechanic from Canada Dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.49,0:17:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这面包真棒\NThis bread is very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.86,0:17:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好吃吧  -好吃\N- Good, eh? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这样的爱尔兰人是在哪学的意大利语\NWhere did an Irisher like you learn to speak Italian?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在意大利  二战的时候\NIn Italy - the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.57,0:17:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意大利哪里\NWhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.36,0:17:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨莱诺\NSalerno.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安齐奥\NAnzio.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.82,0:17:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西西里岛\NSicily...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.20,0:17:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡塔尼亚附近\Naround Catania.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡塔尼亚  我就是卡塔尼亚人\NCatania? I'm from Catania.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  我就觉得你有点卡塔尼亚口音\NYeah? I thought you had an accent like Catania.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你参战了多久\NHow long were you in the war?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.45,0:17:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四年\NFour years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,411天在战场上\N411 days in combat...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,122天在安齐奥\N122 at Anzio.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.45,0:17:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,45步兵团的\NForty-fifth Infantry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.40,0:17:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的天\NMinchia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是啊  -天啊\N- Yeah. - Minchia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.42,0:18:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对的\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.15,0:18:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你当时怕死吗\NWere you afraid of dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.45,0:18:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直很怕\NAlways afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是有人说他不怕可千万别信\NAnd don't let anybody tell you that they weren't afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-那纯属胡扯  知道吗  -是啊\N- That's a lot of bullshit. You know? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人人都很害怕  而且会经常祈祷\NEverybody's afraid. And you pray a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就经常祈祷\NI prayed a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.61,0:18:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我祈祷说  要是能活着离开\NI prayed that I'd never sin again as long as I live
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这辈子一定再也不沾染罪恶\Nif I could just get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.40,0:18:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但紧接着战斗就开始了\NBut then the fighting starts
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就把一切都忘了\Nand then you forget about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.11,0:18:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只想活下来  保住小命\NYou're just trying to survive, stay alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.65,0:18:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当我明白自己撑过了战争时\NOnce I saw that I was getting through the war,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.36,0:18:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看了看自己的周围  说...\NI looked around me, I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.99,0:18:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说  "从现在起  一切顺其自然"\NI said, "From now on, whatever happens, happens."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.36,0:18:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听天由命  去他的\NChe successe successe. Fuck it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.65,0:18:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你懂的  你接到命令就得奉命行事\NYou know, you got orders, you follow them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.28,0:18:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们让你带几个俘虏去树林里\NThey tell you to bring some prisoners into... into the woods,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.49,0:18:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们并不会告诉你该怎么做\Nyou know, and they don't tell you what to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:18:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们只说  "动作快点"\NBut they just say, you know, "Hurry up."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说来疯狂  但我一直不能理解\NIt's crazy, but I never understood
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.32,0:19:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们怎么会乖乖听话\Nhow they would just keep digging
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.15,0:19:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挖自己的坟墓\Ntheir own graves, you know. I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.61,0:19:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停\NStop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.36,0:19:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上来\NRaus!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.99,0:19:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能他们觉得如果干得好\NWell, I mean, maybe they thought if they did a good job,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.90,0:19:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个拿枪的人\Nthe guy with the gun
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.95,0:19:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就会改变主意\Nwould change his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗素  他立刻就对我有了好感\NRussell, he... he took a shine to me right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不久之后\NAfter a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.32,0:19:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就开始给我分派些小任务了\Nhe started giving me little things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.07,0:19:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过那时候  安吉洛本人\NBut then Angelo himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.32,0:19:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也开始交给我一些小任务了\Nhe started giving me little things to do too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.49,0:20:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗素的老婆  凯丽\NRuss's wife, Carrie,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的家族很久很久以前\Nher family goes all the way back, way, way back
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.15,0:20:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在西西里岛跟巴法利诺家族是一个镇上的\Nto the same town in Sicily as the Bufalinos.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们总会谈论这事\NThey talked about it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她来自黑帮中的皇室  可以这么说\NShe came from mob royalty, if you want to call it that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.15,0:20:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希安德拉家族
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希安德拉家族  对他们来说  就好像他们是早期\NThe Sciandras. To them, it was like they came over on the...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.03,0:20:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乘坐意大利五月花号来到美国的\Nthe Italian Mayflower.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.05,0:20:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五月花号是英国移民驶往北美的\N一艘最为著名的船只
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你上楼去吧  清洗一下\NWhy don't you go upstairs, wash up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.99,0:20:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衣服给我  我去处理\NGive me those clothes. I'll get rid of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.03,0:20:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了脱鞋  罗素\NDon't forget your shoes, Russell.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.07,0:21:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗兰克\NHey, Frank,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.99,0:21:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能尽快停车吗\Ncan we stop soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.57,0:21:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问问你老公吧  罗素\NYeah, yeah, well, ask your husband. Russell?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.86,0:21:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他都睡死了\NHe's out cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.32,0:21:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用  我能行\NNo, no, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.57,0:21:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-能行吗  -行\N- Sure? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.24,0:21:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们到哪了\NWhere are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.40,0:21:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快到路易斯堡了\NWe're close to Lewisburg.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.99,0:21:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了告诉我  提醒我一下\NLet me know when we get there. Remind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.70,0:21:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我有几个地方要去  -好的\N- I got some stops to make. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.65,0:21:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗素的生意无所不包\NRussell had a piece of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.20,0:22:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在皮茨顿有家店叫佩恩布帘店\NHe had this store in Pittston called Penn Drape & Curtains.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.95,0:22:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在那里经营着一切生意\NAnd he ran everything out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.65,0:22:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道都有些什么\NWho knew what it all was?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.49,0:22:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他肯定有合伙人\NI mean, I'm sure the man had partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.32,0:22:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种人总是有合伙人的\NThey always have partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.11,0:22:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没人能独占所有钱财\NNobody keeps all the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.24,0:22:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但人人都听罗素的  这点我能确定\NBut everybody listened to Russ. That I can tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.53,0:22:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想贿赂一个法官  先问问罗素\NYou wanted to bribe a judge, you asked Russell.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.24,0:22:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道该贿赂法官多少钱\NYou didn't know how much to bribe him,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.11,0:22:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗素会告诉你\NRussell was gonna tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.61,0:22:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  行  我马上就去\NAll right, all right. I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.15,0:22:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  交给我就行  别担心\NCome on. I'll take care of it. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.11,0:22:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想提拔一个手下\NYou want to promote one of your guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.78,0:22:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗素会告诉你行或不行\NRuss would tell you you could or you could not.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.40,0:22:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮我个忙\NDo me a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.78,0:22:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟史蒂夫去他那  带上维托\NGo with Steve down to his place. Take Vito with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.40,0:22:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那边逗留一会\NAnd just hang around for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.65,0:22:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有几个家伙一直来找麻烦  摆平他们\NThese guys keep coming around, so straighten them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.90,0:22:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我会处理的  罗素  -好的\N- I'll take care of it, Russ. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.40,0:22:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-谢谢  -不客气\N- Thank you. - No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.61,0:22:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那谁...你在这里\NWhere's... Oh, here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.78,0:22:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里\NI'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.74,0:22:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想让某人消失\NYou want to make somebody disappear,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.45,0:22:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得争得罗素的同意\Nyou got to get Russell's permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.36,0:22:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有第二条路\NYou know, no two ways about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.11,0:22:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不  我一点都不担心  -我想也是\N- No, I wasn't worried. - I didn't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.07,0:22:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-帮我给你父亲带个好  -我会的  谢谢\N- Tell your father I said "Hi." - I'll tell him. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.90,0:23:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么还在这里  我刚跟布鲁诺说了\NWhat are you doing here? I just told Bruno.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.57,0:23:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得跟布鲁诺一起去\NYou gotta go with Bruno.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.65,0:23:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好的  我马上去  -去吧  小心\N- Oh, yeah. Yeah, I'm on my way. - Yeah. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.32,0:23:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而当你为罗素办事时\NAnd when you did something for Russ,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.24,0:23:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得亲力亲为\Nyou did it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.03,0:23:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正如罗素常说的\NLike Russ used to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.90,0:23:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我让人替我去处理事情的时候\NWhen I ask somebody to take care of something for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.28,0:23:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望他们能亲自处理\NI expect them to take care of it themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.70,0:23:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要几个人处理同一件事\NI don't need two roads coming back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.75,0:24:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佩恩布帘店
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.57,0:24:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔伯特・安纳斯塔夏\N黑手党"谋杀集团"首领\N1957年死于纽约一家理发店
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.57,0:24:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安纳斯塔夏在理发店被杀时\NWhen Anastasia got killed in the barbershop,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.49,0:24:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗素被请出来安定人心\Nit was Russell they brought in to calm things down,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.24,0:24:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好让大家不要大开杀戒\Nso that everybody wasn't just going around killing everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.99,0:24:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并把事情摆平\Nand it could all get straightened out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.57,0:24:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们知道出了什么事\NWe know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.28,0:24:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也无能为力  木已成舟\NWe can't change it. It is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.36,0:24:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请转告我的朋友  我很乐意帮忙\NPlease tell my friend I'm happy to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.11,0:24:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光看外表你永远猜不到他的身份\NYou'd never know it by looking at this guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.86,0:24:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但条条大路通罗素\Nbut all roads led back to Russ.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.65,0:24:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钱在哪里\NWhere's the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.82,0:24:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他没有  -他没有\N- He don't have it. - He don't have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.07,0:24:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说了点他妈妈的事...\NHe said something about his mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.45,0:25:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停  别跟我说\NStop. Don't tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.53,0:25:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我猜猜\NLet me guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.03,0:25:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他妈死了  然后葬礼花了他一大笔钱\NHis mother died and the funeral set him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.61,0:25:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是不是  -对  完全正确\N- Yeah? - Yeah. Exactly. Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.02,0:25:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他该死的老娘\NHis fucking mother's...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.65,0:25:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在过去十年死了又死\Nfucking dying over and over for the last ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.45,0:25:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要怎么办\NWhat do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.41,0:25:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留在这里\NDon't leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.25,0:25:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿着\NHere.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.28,0:25:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给他看看  别用\NJust show it to him. Don't use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.14,0:25:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看\NLook.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.87,0:25:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗兰克\NHey, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.82,0:25:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瘦子想见你  上车\NSkinny wants to see you. You get in the car.
