Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.53,1:03:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们不知道他对我紧追不舍吗\NYou don't know that they're hounding me?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.34,1:03:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们监视我做的每件事\NThey're looking at everything I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.95,1:03:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们却让这发生在大庭广众之下\NAnd you let this happen in public!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.33,1:04:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们成全了他\NYou're giving it to him!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.68,1:04:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去坐牢了  懂吗\NI'm going to jail. You understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.66,1:04:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜你们所赐  我要去坐牢了\NI'm going to prison because of you,
