Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.21,1:04:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你们想要的  你们想让我进监狱\NThis is what you wanted. You wanted to put me in jail.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.48,1:04:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我  好让我就地杀了你们\NTell me now so I can kill you right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.31,1:04:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就地\NRight here!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.60,1:04:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪\NWhere're you going?
