Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.41,1:04:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我蠢货\NYou gonna call me a motherfucker?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.15,1:04:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以这么跟他们说话  但跟我不行\NYou can talk to them like that, you can't talk to me like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.67,1:04:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗兰克  不  我没说你  你...\NFrank. No! That didn't apply to you. What are you...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.61,1:04:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-没说我  -是的\N- Didn't apply? - No!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.12,1:04:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你要告诉我你没在说我\NThen you gotta let me know it didn't apply to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.88,1:04:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就站在那\NI'm standing right there.
