Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.09,1:04:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就站在那  吉米\NI was standing right there, Jimmy.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.55,1:04:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你胡扯什么呢\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.55,1:04:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我没在说你  我还能说什么\NBut it didn't apply to you! What else can I say?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.92,1:04:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有问题的话  就先把我拉到一边\NYou got a problem, you pull me aside.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.27,1:04:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能辱骂了我然后又说你没在说我\NYou don't insult me and then you say it didn't apply to me.
