Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.01,1:05:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都在掌控之中  别担心\NI'm controlling everything. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.21,1:05:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是当然  当然  我...你懂的\NBut certainly, certainly, I... you know.
