Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.49,1:07:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把车留在那里\NYou leave it there.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.61,1:07:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个叫亨特的大耳朵家伙会在那里等你\NA guy with big ears named Hunt will meet you there.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.86,1:07:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他会给你一辆车  让你开回费城\NHe's gonna give you a car to drive back to Philly.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.62,1:08:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看什么呢\NWhat are you looking at?
