Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.04,1:08:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.30,1:08:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做了手术  所以谁都不需要\NI had an operation, so there's no need for anyone
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.00,1:08:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再看我的耳朵了\Nlooking at my ears anymore.
