Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.52,1:08:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你走吧  赶紧的\NGet out of here. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.93,1:09:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...在猪湾空降\N...unfolded in the Bay of Pigs.
