Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.68,1:09:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其中包含一个旅的兵力和重要军火\Ncarrying a brigade of men and vital ammunition.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.27,1:09:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滩头阵地无法扩大\NThe beachhead could not be enlarged
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.03,1:09:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伞兵们很快便试图杀回\Nand paratroopers were soon trying to fight their way back
