Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.94,1:09:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里的入侵者已经被压制\Nwhere the invaders were pinned down.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.75,1:09:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1500人被留在岸边  没有空中掩护\N1,500 men had been dumped on a shore without air cover
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.66,1:09:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也没有舰炮掩护\Nor protective fire from ships.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.47,1:09:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡斯特罗只需等到他们弹尽粮绝\NCastro had to wait only until they ran out of ammunition
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.04,1:09:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可将他们一举歼灭\Nbefore mopping them up.
