Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.56,1:40:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他以为自己是谁  明星埃罗尔・弗林吗\NWho does he think he is, Errol Flynn?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.36,1:40:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他跟所有人和事对着干\NHe went against everything and everybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.27,1:40:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不在乎\NJust didn't give a shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.84,1:40:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年轻的时候  他绑架了自己的老大\NAnd, growing up, he kidnapped his own bosses.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.53,1:40:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道他是怎么逃脱的\NI don't know how he got away with that.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.25,1:40:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般人没法逃脱  绑架老大就是死路一条\NYou don't get away with that. You do that, you die.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.51,1:40:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这么简单\NThat simple.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.62,1:40:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他坐牢的时候\NWhen he went away to the can,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.09,1:40:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,招募了黑人而不是白人\Nhe recruited black guys instead of his own kind.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.01,1:40:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等他出狱  没人知道他在做什么\NAnd when he got out, nobody knew what he was doing,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.03,1:40:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟谁一起做\Nor who he was doing with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.28,1:40:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不知道是什么情况  没人知道\NWe didn't know what the hell was going on. Nobody did.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.30,1:40:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不喜欢他的做法\NAnd if you don't like what he's doing,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.06,1:40:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你出声抱怨\Nand you say something,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.36,1:40:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后你就等着看会发生什么吧\Nthen you see what happens.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.69,1:41:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意大利裔美国人人权联盟
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.46,1:41:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁会做那种事  谁会那么办事\NWho does something like that? Who does things like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.47,1:41:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉你\NI'll tell you. I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.19,1:41:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个无赖\NThis disgraziato.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.75,1:41:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他和奥斯瓦尔德是一类的\NHim and Oswald. Two of a kind.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.11,1:41:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少在达拉斯  那些孩子不在\NAt least in Dallas, the kids weren't there.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.57,1:41:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有杰姬\NIt was just Jackie.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.94,1:41:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乔伊  你的医生打来电话  你一小时之前死了\NJoey, your doctor called. You died an hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.39,1:41:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是犹太人吗\NYou a Jewish fellow?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.92,1:41:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想当犹太人吗\NWould you like to be?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.09,1:41:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别担心割礼  现在不会那么做了\NDon't worry about the operation. We don't do that no more.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.62,1:41:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在会先打麻药\NWe freeze it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.32,1:41:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就站着什么都不用做\NAnd you stand there and don't do anything
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.89,1:41:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个墨西哥婆娘拿着块湿石头走过来\Nand a Mexican broad comes over with a wet rock.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.01,1:41:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啪\NThwack!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.61,1:41:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大笑没问题  我开所有人的玩笑\NSee, it's okay to laugh. I make fun of everybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.97,1:41:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝带我们来到世上就是为了让我们笑\NThat's why God put us on this earth, to laugh.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.93,1:41:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都是我的讽刺对象\NI work everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.16,1:41:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我开黑人玩笑  我开犹太人玩笑\NI make fun of blacks, I make fun of Jews.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.41,1:41:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉普赛人  意大利人\NI work Gypsies, I work Italians.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.77,1:41:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些意大利人可不行\NWell, not those Italians.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.18,1:42:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不不\NNo, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.70,1:42:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  乔伊  我有钱  别开枪\NIt's okay, Joey. I got the money. Don't shoot.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.93,1:42:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们今天告诉我\NI was told today,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.27,1:42:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"说话千万小心"\N"Be very careful about what you say."
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.75,1:42:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但抛开那些玩笑  生日快乐  乔伊\NBut, uh, all kidding aside, happy birthday, Joey.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.18,1:42:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗素\NRuss.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.16,1:42:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你戴那个干什么\NWhat are you doing with that?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.48,1:42:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意大利裔美国人人权联盟
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.16,1:42:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真相信那个狗屁联盟\NYou really believe in that bullshit league?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:34.66,1:42:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是因为那个\NWell, it's not that.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.56,1:42:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是意大利裔\NIt's Italian.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.52,1:42:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乔伊  乔伊\NJoey. Joey.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.44,1:42:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我说什么了  -不不不\N- What did I say? - Oh, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.88,1:42:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我说什么了  -乔伊  乔伊\N- What did I say? - Joey, Joey. Joey. Joey.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.52,1:42:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听我说\NNow, listen.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.72,1:42:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能在这儿说那种话  明白吗  不行\NYou can't say that stuff like that here. Okay? You can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.22,1:42:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  只有瑞克斯能开玩笑吗\NWhy not? Rickles is the only one who can make jokes?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.17,1:42:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是老大\NThe man's a boss.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.37,1:42:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是老大  他是老大\NSo I'm a boss. He's a boss.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.93,1:42:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们应该是兄弟  对吧\NWe're all supposed to be brothers, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.03,1:42:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你是老大\NI know you're a boss.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.91,1:42:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  但我们现在不想吵  对吧\NI know, but we don't wanna have a beef now. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.82,1:42:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我们是兄弟  对吧  -没错  兄弟\N- We're brothers, right? - That's right, brothers.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:57.86,1:42:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我们是兄弟吧  -你们是兄弟\N- We're brothers? - You're brothers.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.72,1:43:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我们是兄弟  -我不跟你争\N- We're brothers. - I'm not arguing with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.32,1:43:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是兄弟\NEverybody's a brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.33,1:43:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错  你是兄弟  你是他兄弟\NThat's right, you're a brother. You're his brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.37,1:43:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是  但你们是\NI'm not, but you guys are.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.65,1:43:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以如果你能给点面子就好了\NSo that's why I would like it if you just...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.98,1:43:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好  -好吗\N- All right. - Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.90,1:43:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我们是兄弟  -对\N- We're brothers? - You're brothers.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.11,1:43:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对  今天我过生日\NYeah. It's my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.34,1:43:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生日快乐\NHappy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.18,1:43:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生日快乐\NHappy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.96,1:43:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧滚吧\NGet the fuck out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.51,1:43:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要做这种活儿\NNow, for something like this,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.37,1:43:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你需要两把枪\Nyou're gonna need two guns.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.14,1:43:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一把是用的  一把是后备\NThe one you're gonna use and a backup.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.83,1:43:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要比点22口径的更有威慑力\NYou want something with more stopping power than a .22.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.72,1:43:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不用消音器\NYou definitely don't want a silencer.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.79,1:44:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要弄出很大响声  吓得目击者逃走\NYou want to make a lot of noise to make the witnesses run away
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.69,1:44:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样他们就不会看你了\Nso they ain't gonna be looking at you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.50,1:44:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但点45口径的响声可不行\NBut not the noise a .45 makes
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.51,1:44:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样动静就太大了\N'cause that makes too much noise,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.06,1:44:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几个街区外的巡逻警车都能听到\Nand a patrol car can hear it a few blocks away at least.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.83,1:44:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警察管点32口径的叫女士枪  因为它比较好控制\NThe cops call a .32 a woman's gun because it's easier to handle
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.67,1:44:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有点38口径的破坏力\Nand don't do the damage a .38 does,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.74,1:44:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是足够了\Nbut, you know, it does enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.88,1:44:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安贝特蛤蜊餐厅
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.68,1:44:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到时候是深夜  爱达荷州的游客不会在那儿\NIt would be late, so the tourists from Idaho
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.04,1:44:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们已经睡觉了\Nwouldn't be there. They'd be in bed.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:39.13,1:44:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在小意大利区\NAnd him being down there in Little Italy,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.35,1:44:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许会更自在  更放松\Nmaybe he'd be more comfortable, more relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.63,1:44:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天是他生日  所以他会带着老婆孩子一起去\NIt was his birthday so he'd be there with his wife
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.69,1:44:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样正好\Nand his kid which, in this case,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.09,1:44:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这正是我们的目的\Nthat's good because that's the point.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.41,1:44:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该让他们亲眼见识\NThey should have to see what it's like.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.28,1:44:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他已经喝了不少酒\NHe'd already been drinking,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.25,1:45:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样他会迟缓很多\Nwhich would have slowed him down a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.44,1:45:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的保镖会跟着他\NHis bodyguard would be with him
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.71,1:45:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乔伊自己也应该是带着枪的\Nand Joey himself could be carrying, too,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:05.68,1:45:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他的枪可能在他老婆的包里\Nbut then the piece would be in his wife's purse probably.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.09,1:45:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从来不会事先对你透露多少\NYou never got a lot of advance notice.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:18.44,1:45:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只知道你到时候要做什么\NAll you knew was your part of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.61,1:45:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,红发约翰只知道\NJohn the Redhead knew only one thing:
Dialogue: 0,1:45:25.66,1:45:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他要开车送我过去\Nhe was gonna drop me off,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.60,1:45:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绕着街区转  然后再接我\Ncircle the block and pick me up.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.32,1:45:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安贝特蛤蜊餐厅
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.75,1:45:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得先解决掉保镖\NYou wanna take out the bodyguard first.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.30,1:45:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是杀他  别杀他  让他失去行动能力就好\NNot kill him. Don't kill him, just disable him.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.87,1:45:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟他无冤无仇\NYou got no argument with him,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.31,1:45:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以别照着脸或者胸膛来一枪\Nso, not in the face or the chest.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:50.39,1:45:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时  干这种活儿\NSometimes, with something like this,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.13,1:45:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可能想先去趟厕所\Nyou might want to go to the bathroom first.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.28,1:45:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好确定没人跟踪你进来\NIt gives you a chance to make sure nobody followed you in.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.29,1:46:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也能让你确定\NIt also gives you a chance to make sure
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.70,1:46:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无需担心厕所里的人\Nnobody is in the bathroom you have to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:03.90,1:46:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也给你机会上趟厕所\NIt also gives you a chance to go to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.22,1:46:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干活的时候你不想不舒服\NYou don't want to be uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.66,1:46:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我之前去过  深夜在这么个小餐厅\NBut I went before, and in a place this small, this late,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.98,1:46:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直接干活就行了\Nyou might as well just get to work.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.11,1:46:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来点红酒\NWe need more wine, all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.77,1:46:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汤米  再来点红酒\NTommy, some more wine.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.75,1:46:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后呢\NSo how about after?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:18.64,1:46:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-蛋糕  蛋糕  蛋糕  -现在还不行\N- Cake, cake, cake! - Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.89,1:46:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还没吃完饭呢\NYou're not even done eating the meal yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.27,1:46:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要蛋糕  得了吧  不能这样\NYou want the cake? Come on, you can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.86,1:46:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠\NShit!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.94,1:46:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,操  操\NFuck! Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.38,1:47:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此事发生在纽约的小意大利区\NIt happened in New York's Little Italy,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.39,1:47:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传言这里是黑帮的中立地带\Nan area rumored to be neutral territory among mobsters.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.70,1:47:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安贝特蛤蜊餐厅
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.71,1:47:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凶杀之后\NAfter the killing,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:11.46,1:47:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警方找到了几把枪以及一些指纹\Npolice found several guns and some fingerprints
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.19,1:47:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今日正在追查\Nwhich they were tracing today.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:16.09,1:47:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"疯子乔"乔瑟夫・加洛\NJoseph "Crazy Joe" Gallo
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.47,1:47:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚间来到这家温馨的海鲜餐厅\Nhad come to the intimate seafood restaurant to cap an evening of celebration
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.84,1:47:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与他结婚不满一个月的妻子\Nwith his new bride of less than a month,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.60,1:47:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及与前妻所生的十一岁女儿一起庆祝\Nand his 11-year-old daughter by a previous marriage.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.44,1:47:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在庆祝乔的47岁生日\NThey were, uh, celebrating Joe's 47th birthday.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.47,1:47:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那晚他们先去了一家夜店\NThey had been to a nightclub early in the evening.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:33.35,1:47:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们坐在餐厅后面的一桌  总共六个人\NThey were sitting at a rear table, this group of six people,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.04,1:47:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后\Nwhen a, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.18,1:47:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个男人从后门进来\Na man walked in from the back door,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.73,1:47:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直接走到\Nand he walked up, uh,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.23,1:47:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走到桌子边上  开了三枪\Nto the side of the table. He fired three shots.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.61,1:47:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他打了乔两枪\NHe hit Joe twice
Dialogue: 0,1:47:50.29,1:47:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-还打了他的保镖  -佩琪  走吧\N- and he hit his bodyguard... - Peggy, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:52.29,1:47:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希腊人皮特一枪\N...Pete the Greek, one time.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:54.50,1:47:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一共开了十四枪\NThere was a total of 14 shots fired.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:57.11,1:47:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佩琪  走吧\NPeggy, come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.75,1:48:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乔伊・加洛的地盘总统街上\NIt's quiet here on President Street,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:00.78,1:48:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常安静\NJoey Gallo's turf.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.98,1:48:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至有些太安静了\NIn fact, it's too quiet.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.99,1:48:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在布鲁克林\NOut here in Brooklyn,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.10,1:48:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乔伊・加洛是个英雄\NJoey Gallo was a hero.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:07.55,1:48:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,据猜测  他的死亡或将引发一场帮派战争\NSpeculation has it that his death may start a gang war,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.33,1:48:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能已经悄然开始\Nif it hasn't already begun.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:13.81,1:48:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,普通汽油
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.69,1:48:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,电话亭
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.27,1:48:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你好好的  吉米  -你也是  麦奇\N- Take it easy, Jimmy. - You too, Mikey.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.57,1:48:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保重了  吉米\NTake good care, Jimmy.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.18,1:48:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以防再也不见  问个好\NIf I don't see you again, hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.60,1:48:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四年后  花了五十万美元\NFour years later and $500,000 under the table
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.05,1:48:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贿赂尼克松的连任委员会\Nto Nixon's re-election committee,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:58.01,1:49:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米终于得偿所愿\NJimmy finally got what he wanted.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:00.07,1:49:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  不过我不会再回来了\NSorry, but I won't be back.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.66,1:49:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总统特赦以及假释\NA presidential pardon and his parole.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.77,1:49:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米\NJimmy!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.72,1:49:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在打算做什么  吉米\NWhat are you gonna do now, Jimmy?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.21,1:49:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要做的第一件事就是\NWell, the first thing I'm gonna do is register
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.23,1:49:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去联邦缓刑办公室登记\Nwith the Federal Probation Office,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.02,1:49:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后就和我妻子一起去佛州晒太阳\Nand then I'm going down to Florida with my wife to get some sun.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.34,1:49:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那之后有什么计划吗\NAny plans after that?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.61,1:49:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要夺回我工会的控制权\NYeah, I'm gonna take back control of my union.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.36,1:49:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要怎么做  吉米\NHow're you gonna do that, Jimmy?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.37,1:49:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲茨也要竞选  你感觉怎么样\NHow do you like Fitz running against you?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:26.20,1:49:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉不好\NI don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:26.83,1:49:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米  被关这么久是什么感觉\NJimmy, what was it like being locked up all that time?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:29.09,1:49:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常好  我很开心\NIt was wonderful. Had a great time.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:30.47,1:49:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卢姆餐厅
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.34,1:49:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做的第一件事就是\NThe first thing I did was,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.55,1:49:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去卢姆餐厅买了几个辣味热狗\NI picked up some chili dogs from Lum's,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:35.53,1:49:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米爱热狗就像爱冰激淋\Nwhich Jimmy loved almost as much as ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:37.91,1:49:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,理查德・尼克松总统\NA consultant to President
Dialogue: 0,1:49:39.23,1:49:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连任竞选委员会的一名顾问\NRichard Nixon's re-election campaign committee...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.18,1:49:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们的秘诀就是用啤酒蒸香肠\NThe secret is they steam them in beer.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:44.50,1:49:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是全美最好吃的热狗\NThere ain't a better hot dog in America.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:46.60,1:49:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警方称麦考德和他的同谋\NPolice say McCord and his accomplices
Dialogue: 0,1:49:48.75,1:49:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随身带了电子监听设备\Nbrought electronic listening devices with them
Dialogue: 0,1:49:51.17,1:49:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还卸下了两块天花板\Nand had removed two ceiling panels...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:52.79,1:49:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卢姆餐厅
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.95,1:49:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以便在民主党全国委员会\N...while installing eavesdropping equipment
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.17,1:49:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安装窃听设备\Nat the Democratic National Committee.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:58.31,1:50:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡车司机工会
Dialogue: 0,1:49:58.90,1:50:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看看  他还真有胆子竞选工会主席\NLook at this. He's got the balls to run for President of the Teamsters.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:01.93,1:50:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看看  托尼・普罗还给他颁奖了\NLook at this. And Tony Pro giving him an award.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:04.63,1:50:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这混蛋  你信吗\NThis fuck... Do you believe it?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.33,1:50:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡车司机工会
Dialogue: 0,1:50:06.23,1:50:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲茨很受特定人群的欢迎\NLook, Fitz is very popular with certain people.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.01,1:50:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡车司机工会
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.16,1:50:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他当然受欢迎  能不受欢迎吗\NOf course he's popular. Who wouldn't be popular?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:11.00,1:50:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪个弟兄问他借钱他都给\NHe loans money to every goombah who asks.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.71,1:50:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以托尼支持他  他把选票都给菲茨了\NThat's why Tony's behind him. He's given Fitz all his votes.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:16.85,1:50:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你受工会大多数人的支持\NYou got great support from most of the union.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.06,1:50:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只需要托尼・普罗\NAll you need is Tony Pro's
Dialogue: 0,1:50:20.51,1:50:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在东北部的选民  你就能赢\Nvoters in the Northeast, and you can win.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:22.36,1:50:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你真不要吃一个吗  -不了  谢谢\N- You sure you don't want one of these? - No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.48,1:50:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是不敢相信我要去找托尼・普罗要选票\NI just can't believe I gotta go to Tony Pro to get votes.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.55,1:50:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这都什么跟什么\NWhat is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:31.63,1:50:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托尼牢牢控制着菲茨  吉米\NTony has Fitz in his pocket, Jimmy.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:33.91,1:50:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工会不受黑帮控制\NWise guys don't run the union.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:35.47,1:50:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有菲茨就行\NWith Fitz, they do.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.90,1:50:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米  等你重新当上主席\NJimmy, listen, as soon as you're back as president,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:40.37,1:50:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想做什么就做什么\Nyou can do anything you want to.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:41.49,1:50:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想解雇谁就解雇谁\NYou can fire anybody you want to.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:43.34,1:50:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把托尼・普罗解雇了都行\NYou can even fire Tony Pro.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.05,1:50:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以盯着他  让他清空桌子\NYou could stand over him, watch him clear out his desk.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:49.69,1:50:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还可以让他脱光  搜他的身\NYou could strip-search the guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.29,1:50:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确保他走的时候连个回形针都带不走\NMake sure he doesn't walk off with a paper clip.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.67,1:50:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对  听见没  你听见没\NYes. See that? Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.16,1:50:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都以为乔是白脸\NSee, everybody thinks Jo's the nice one
Dialogue: 0,1:50:59.93,1:51:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是黑脸\Nand I'm the bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:01.50,1:51:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但其实是反过来\NBut it's opposite.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:03.68,1:51:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是大灰狼  我是小绵羊\NShe's the killer and I'm the sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:07.78,1:51:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我要去和狗杂种讲和了\NNow I gotta make peace with the cocksucker.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:11.56,1:51:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你重归于好\NI want to make up with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:13.69,1:51:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你支持我  拜托了  托尼\NI need you to endorse me. Please, Tony.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:16.81,1:51:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求你了\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:18.19,1:51:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死\NFucking...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:20.49,1:51:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这事我做不来\NI'm not gonna get through this.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:21.67,1:51:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟他谈谈就可以了\NYou gotta talk to him, that's all. Just...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:24.06,1:51:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得处理好\NYou gotta deal with it, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:24.95,1:51:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顺其自然吧\NLet the chips fall where they may.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:26.09,1:51:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过他真是个狗杂种\NHe is a cocksucker, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:28.98,1:51:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我坐下和他谈  你一起来吗\NIf I sat down with him, would you come along?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:31.10,1:51:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢  当然了\NWhat are you talking about? Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:32.71,1:51:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么会不跟你去\NHow am I not gonna go with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:43.65,1:51:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈的  走吧\NFuck it. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:44.69,1:51:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米  吉米  给个机会\NJimmy, Jimmy. Give it a chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:46.58,1:51:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给个机会  再等几分钟\NGive it a chance. Give it a few more minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:50.68,1:51:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-就  -这样不行\N- Just... - This isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:52.01,1:51:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样不行  怎么能这样\NThis isn't right. You don't do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:54.11,1:51:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能让人干等\NYou don't keep a man waiting.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:56.13,1:51:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  我知道\NI know. I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:58.60,1:51:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真要让人等\NThe only time you do
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.59,1:52:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就代表你有话要说\Nis when you want to say something.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:03.90,1:52:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我知道  -你想说"去死"\N- I know. - When you want to say "Fuck you."
Dialogue: 0,1:52:06.47,1:52:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有这种解释\NThat's the only time.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:09.14,1:52:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了\NHere they are.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:11.81,1:52:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能相信这天气吗  弗兰克\NCan you believe this weather, Frank? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:14.18,1:52:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外面快三十度了  真好\NIt's 85 degrees outside. Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:17.64,1:52:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是托尼・杰克\NTony Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:19.39,1:52:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是吉米\NJimmy.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:20.13,1:52:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,纽约的人都要冻死了  看看我们\NPeople freezing to death in New York and look at us, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:23.86,1:52:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就想知道  我们干嘛不一直住在这里\NWhy we don't live here all year round is what I wanna know.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:26.78,1:52:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了\NBeautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.21,1:52:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-这是夏天  -什么\N- It's summer. - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:31.02,1:52:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是夏天\NIt's summer.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:33.23,1:52:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,纽约的人没要冻死\NPeople aren't freezing to death in New York.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:36.67,1:52:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在是夏天\NIt's summer.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:40.46,1:52:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我心里  纽约一直零下十三度\NIn my mind, it's always eight degrees in New York.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.44,1:52:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就想表个态\NI'm making a point.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:44.24,1:52:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想表个态\NYou're making a point.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:46.06,1:52:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿成这样表态\NMaking a point dressing like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:48.41,1:52:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你开会就穿成这样吗\NIs that how you dress for a meeting?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:51.46,1:52:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在佛州就穿成这样吗  穿西装\NThis is how you dress in Florida? In a suit?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.86,1:52:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去开会吗\NFor a meeting?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:56.90,1:53:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别说佛州  不管在什么鬼地方\NAnywhere. Florida, Timbuktu, I dress in a suit.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:00.50,1:53:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我开会都穿西装\NFor a meetin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.49,1:53:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-而且你迟到了  -什么\N- And you're late. - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:05.23,1:53:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你迟到了\NYou're late.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:08.40,1:53:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  路上堵车\NYeah, there was traffic.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:09.75,1:53:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  堵车\NYes, traffic.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.71,1:53:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是堵车了\NWasn't there traffic?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:12.59,1:53:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-来堵车这一套  -的确堵车\N- You give me traffic? - There was traffic.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.23,1:53:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想要我们怎么办\NWhat do you want from us?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:15.74,1:53:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保险杠都抵着保险杠了\NIt was bumper to fuckin' bumper.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:16.59,1:53:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  堵车确实严重\NYeah, yeah. No, it's bad, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:18.67,1:53:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,堵车\NTraffic.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.57,1:53:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这辈子从来没有\NI never waited for anyone who was late
Dialogue: 0,1:53:24.26,1:53:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等人超过十分钟\Nmore than ten minutes in my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:27.25,1:53:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十五分钟吧  比较合适\NI'd say fifteen. Fifteen's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:29.25,1:53:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  十分钟\NNo, ten.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:31.59,1:53:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得不行  十分钟不够\NI don't think so, ten's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:33.50,1:53:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得算上堵车的时间\NYou have to take traffic into account.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:35.02,1:53:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我算了  堵车的时间算进去了\NThat's what I'm doing. I'm taking traffic into account.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:38.84,1:53:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以给了十分钟\NThat's why it's ten.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:40.01,1:53:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我还是坚持十五分钟  -十分钟\N- I still say 15. - No, ten.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:42.97,1:53:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行吧  这点我们保留意见\NFine. We disagree on that.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:45.10,1:53:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不就十二分半\NHow about twelve and a half minutes?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:46.98,1:53:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就对了  十二分半\NThere we go, 12.5.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:48.19,1:53:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中间值  正中间  太好了\NThe middle. Right in the middle. Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:50.71,1:53:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超过十分钟\NMore than ten...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:53.13,1:53:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是有话要说了\Nyou're saying something.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:55.66,1:53:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你有话要对我说吗  -我来了\N- You saying something to me? - I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:59.00,1:53:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这个意思\NIt says what it says.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:01.82,1:54:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就这样吧\NSo there it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:05.04,1:54:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来怎么谈\NWhere do we go from here?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:09.05,1:54:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能为你做什么\NWell, what can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:13.81,1:54:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你\NI want you...
