Dialogue: 0,2:02:10.37,2:02:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卖给了他的黑社会朋友\Nto his underworld pals.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:12.35,2:02:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑帮控制着他\NThe mob controls him,
Dialogue: 0,2:02:14.08,2:02:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那意味着他们也控制着我们的养老金\Nwhich means it controls our pension fund.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:16.57,2:02:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说的是上十亿美元的低息或无息贷款\NI'm talking about a billion dollars in low or no-interest loans
Dialogue: 0,2:02:20.49,2:02:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都被他借给了已知的黑帮分子\Nthis man has given to known racketeers
Dialogue: 0,2:02:23.24,2:02:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用到他们非法勾当中\Nfor their illegal enterprises.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:24.98,2:02:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再也不可能了\NNot anymore.
