Dialogue: 0,2:02:50.35,2:02:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他该做什么吗  罗素\NYou know what he should do, Russ?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:52.44,2:02:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他应该将他那一大笔养老金提现\NHe should cash in that big pension of his.
