Dialogue: 0,2:03:27.00,2:03:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是认为他应该...\NWe just think that he should...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:29.80,2:03:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,享受陪伴孙辈的日子\Nmaybe enjoy his grandchildren,
Dialogue: 0,2:03:31.73,2:03:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,享受养老金  享受目前的生活"\Nenjoy his pension, enjoy his life as is."
Dialogue: 0,2:03:34.19,2:03:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用再说了  弗兰克\NGo no further, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:37.82,2:03:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁说的\NWho said it?
