Dialogue: 0,2:03:50.86,2:03:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是他吗  真不是吗\NNot him. No?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:52.70,2:03:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁\NThen who?
