Dialogue: 0,2:03:59.50,2:04:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托尼\NTony?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:00.69,2:04:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪个托尼\NWhich Tony?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:02.02,2:04:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么多人叫托尼\NThey're all named Tony.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:04.08,2:04:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意大利人是怎么回事\NI mean, what's the matter with Italians?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:06.42,2:04:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们难道没别的名字取了吗\NThey can only think of one name.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:09.52,2:04:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另一个托尼\NThe other Tony.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:12.51,2:04:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪个\NWhat Tony?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:16.45,2:04:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨雷诺\NSalerno.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:26.29,2:04:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能说什么呢\NWell, what can I say?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:29.92,2:04:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米  我这是在帮你\NJimmy, I'm trying to help you.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:31.18,2:04:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-让你明白一些事  -我知道\N- I'm trying to tell you something. - I know you are.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:33.84,2:04:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗兰克  想都别想\NFrank, don't even think about it.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:36.73,2:04:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我向来是有话直说\NI don't keep my mouth shut...
Dialogue: 0,2:04:38.31,2:04:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我知道  -对谁都是如此\N- I know that. - ...for anyone.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:39.77,2:04:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知你知  但他们不知道\NI know that, you know that, they don't know that.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:45.00,2:04:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的为人本性  我也不会做出任何改变\NThat's who I am, that's what I am and that's what I'm gonna do.
