Dialogue: 0,2:06:56.30,2:06:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到六月份\NI did not realize
Dialogue: 0,2:06:57.46,2:06:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才知道霍华德・亨特先生\Nthat Mr. Howard Hunt worked most of the time
Dialogue: 0,2:06:59.63,2:07:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在白宫的大部分时间\Nwhile he was at the White House
Dialogue: 0,2:06:59.75,2:07:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前白宫法律顾问\N约翰・W・迪恩三世
Dialogue: 0,2:07:00.88,2:07:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是在管工部门工作\Nin the plumbers unit until after June...
Dialogue: 0,2:07:02.88,2:07:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是个叛徒  不过...\NHe's a rat, but that's, you know...
Dialogue: 0,2:07:04.55,2:07:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确实是  但他是个精明的叛徒\NHe's a rat. But he's a smart rat.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:09.42,2:07:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉丁赌场  剧院  餐厅
Dialogue: 0,2:07:09.63,2:07:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚这么多人都是来给弗兰克捧场的吧\NWe've got a great crowd for Frank tonight, huh?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:12.17,2:07:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗兰克・希兰\N答谢晚宴\N1973年10月18日
Dialogue: 0,2:07:12.70,2:07:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给他来点掌声\NCome on. Give it up.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:16.84,2:07:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是因为弗兰克广结好友\NThat's because Frank is a man with a lot of friends.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:23.38,2:07:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有在乔治・巴顿将军的带领下\NFrom his war buddies who fought with him in Italy
Dialogue: 0,2:07:25.92,2:07:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与他在意大利并肩作战的战友\Nunder General George Patton...
Dialogue: 0,2:07:29.92,2:07:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有司机  全国工会组织者\Nto the drivers, national organizers,
Dialogue: 0,2:07:33.05,2:07:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屋顶工工会主席\N约翰・麦卡洛\N1980年在自家厨房头中六枪身亡
Dialogue: 0,2:07:33.09,2:07:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,代理商  地方工会主席\Nbusiness agents, local presidents,
Dialogue: 0,2:07:35.96,2:07:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,联合委员会主席  以及区域受托人等等\Njoint committee chairmen, and regional trustees,
Dialogue: 0,2:07:39.75,2:07:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚到场的都是弗兰克的好友\Nwe are all friends of Frank's tonight.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:44.05,2:07:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗兰克的好友\NFriends of Frank.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:47.46,2:07:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如全国有色人种协进会主席塞西尔・摩尔\NLike NAACP president Cecil Moore.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:51.63,2:07:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地方检察官艾米特・菲茨帕特里克\NDistrict Attorney Emmett Fitzpatrick.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:55.13,2:07:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,费城市长弗兰克・里佐\NPhiladelphia mayor Frank Rizzo.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:59.50,2:08:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们都喜欢你呢  弗兰克\NHey, they like you, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:01.38,2:08:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然  还有我们的特邀发言人\NAnd, of course, our featured speaker,
Dialogue: 0,2:08:03.75,2:08:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯・里德尔・霍法\NJames Riddell Hoffa.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:12.92,2:08:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同时呢  在外面的树上\NAnd meanwhile, outside in the trees,
Dialogue: 0,2:08:15.59,2:08:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还藏着联调局的人\Nwe got the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:18.71,2:08:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有谁要去看看吗\NSomebody wanna check on them?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:21.84,2:08:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来分享一下我第一次见到弗兰克时的场景吧\NNow, let me tell you about the first time I met Frank.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:24.00,2:08:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他带我去吃牛排晚餐\NHe took me out to a steak dinner,
Dialogue: 0,2:08:26.13,2:08:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他问我说  "你的牛排要几分熟"\Nand he asked me, he said, "How do you like your steak?"
Dialogue: 0,2:08:28.21,2:08:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说"我喜欢一分熟"  他说"我也是"\NI said, "I like it rare." He said, "Me too."
Dialogue: 0,2:08:29.96,2:08:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后就开始上牛排了  我的是一分熟\NWell, they bring out the steaks. Mine's rare.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:32.50,2:08:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗兰克的那份正从厨房里走出来\NFrank's was still walking from the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:36.46,2:08:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他转身对我说  "其实吧\NHe turns to me, he said, "Well, you know,
Dialogue: 0,2:08:38.38,2:08:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢动物  我不想杀生"\NI'm an animal lover. I don't wanna hurt it."
Dialogue: 0,2:08:42.55,2:08:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他居然喜欢动物\NHe's an animal lover.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:07.96,2:09:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙连主席都没当上\NThis guy is not even the goddamn president
Dialogue: 0,2:09:10.05,2:09:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在拖延别人的贷款了\Nand he's holding up people's loans.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:12.88,2:09:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你确定吗  -我确定\N- Are you sure? - I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:15.25,2:09:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是怎么办到的\NAnd how's he supposed to do that?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:16.25,2:09:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他的手下拖延了\NBecause his guys are holding 'em back loans
Dialogue: 0,2:09:17.84,2:09:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡洛斯在新奥尔良建新酒店的钱\Non Carlos's new hotel in New Orleans,
Dialogue: 0,2:09:19.88,2:09:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在凯撒酒店扩建的钱\Nthe add-on that we're doing at Caesars.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:26.55,2:09:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-菲茨都在做些什么  -菲茨吗\N- And what's Fitz doing all this time? - Fitz?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:28.88,2:09:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  这事应该他管的\NYeah, he's supposed to help with this shit.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:30.84,2:09:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钱是养老基金的受托人出的\NThe money comes from the Pension Fund trustees.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:33.21,2:09:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们应该要签字同意\NThey gotta sign off on it.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:34.55,2:09:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们本应该听菲茨的安排开绿灯\NThey're supposed to be rubber-stamping what Fitz says.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:36.80,2:09:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-没错  -只是吉米\N- Right, right. Yeah. - Except Jimmy
Dialogue: 0,2:09:39.09,2:09:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让其中几位拒绝开绿灯了\Nhas a couple of them to stop rubber-stamping.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:43.55,2:09:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个王八蛋\NThe son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:45.63,2:09:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为已经处理好了\NI thought we took care of that.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:48.42,2:09:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他怎么跟人说的吗\NYou know what he told somebody?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:49.75,2:09:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说一旦菲茨下位  他成功上台\NHe goes, once Fitz is out and he's in,
Dialogue: 0,2:09:51.75,2:09:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就要收回以前的债款\Nhe's gonna call in the old loans.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:54.13,2:09:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,酒店  赌场  房地产之类的\NHotels, casinos, real estate, no matter what it is.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:57.67,2:10:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且你要是没有马上连本带利还钱给他\NAnd if you don't have his money and interest in two seconds,
Dialogue: 0,2:10:00.09,2:10:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就要全部接管\Nhe's taking 'em over.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:01.92,2:10:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能让他得逞\NWe can't have that.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:05.59,2:10:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-这是他说的  -是他说的\N- He said that? - He said that.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:07.67,2:10:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你确定这是他的原话吗  托尼\NYou sure he said that, Tony?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:09.25,2:10:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他的原话\NHe said that.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:10.71,2:10:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说的这些全都是他的原话\NEverything I'm telling you, yeah, he said.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:12.80,2:10:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他以为他是谁啊  卡斯特罗吗\NI mean, who does he think he is? Castro?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:18.42,2:10:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? 就是现在 ?\N? The time is now ?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:20.80,2:10:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? 一同起立欢呼 ?\N? The time to stand and cheer ?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:23.21,2:10:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? 因为留下的都是美好时光 ?\N? 'Cause better times are here to stay ?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:27.17,2:10:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? 昨日已远去 ?\N? Oh, yesterday is over ?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:29.88,2:10:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? 明日要到来 ?\N? Tomorrow's on its way ?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:32.09,2:10:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? 但快来看看今天有什么在等待着你 ?\N? But look what's new and made for you today ?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:37.13,2:10:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? 今天 ?\N? Today ?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:40.25,2:10:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要的不是钱吧\NYou don't need money, do you?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:41.67,2:10:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与钱无关\NIt's not about money.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:43.67,2:10:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是为了钱\NIf it's not about money,
Dialogue: 0,2:10:44.71,2:10:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就真的有点搞不懂了\Nthen I'm really having trouble understanding,
Dialogue: 0,2:10:46.67,2:10:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们谈了那么久到底是为了什么\Nbecause I don't know what all the talk is about.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:49.38,2:10:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的工会\NIt's my union.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:51.80,2:10:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-这很难理解吗  -不是\N- Is that hard to understand? - No, no.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:53.75,2:10:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的工会  没问题  永远都是你的工会\NIt's your union, that's right. It'll always be your union.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:56.30,2:10:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你完全可以下台在幕后管理\NYou could step down and still run it.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:57.88,2:11:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我才不会下台  -你这话什么意思\N- No, you don't step down. - What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:00.09,2:11:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗素  下台是管不了工会的\NRuss, you don't step down to run a union.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:02.13,2:11:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下台是直接进坟墓\NYou step down to go to your grave.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:04.17,2:11:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听好了\NWell, listen.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:06.30,2:11:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还是在想...不好意思\NI still think... I can't help but think, I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,2:11:09.05,2:11:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这么迫切是出于什么其他理由吗\Nbut is there another reason or something?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:11.38,2:11:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的工会  "其他理由"又是什么意思\NThis is my union! What do you mean, "another reason"?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:15.55,2:11:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的工会\NThis is my union.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:17.13,2:11:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吗  你先明确好这一点\NAll right? Let's start with that
Dialogue: 0,2:11:18.84,2:11:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再去弄清楚别的事情\Nand then try to understand things.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:20.75,2:11:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听我说  有人\NListen, some people,
Dialogue: 0,2:11:23.25,2:11:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我  但有人\Nnot me, but some people,
Dialogue: 0,2:11:26.75,2:11:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们有点顾虑\Nthey're a little concerned.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:28.92,2:11:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人  不是我  他们觉得你可能...\NSome people, not me, they think that you might...
Dialogue: 0,2:11:32.71,2:11:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可能什么\NI might...
Dialogue: 0,2:11:33.67,2:11:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可能没有表达出应有的感激之举\NYou might be demonstrating a failure to show appreciation.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:40.34,2:11:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有表现出感激\NI'm not showing appreciation?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:42.71,2:11:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人是这么说的\NAccording to, you know, some people.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:44.80,2:11:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我蹲了五年牢房\NI went to school for five fucking years.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:47.88,2:11:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我知道  -整整五年\N- Yes, you did. - Five fucking years.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:51.84,2:11:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有供出任何一个人\NI didn't name one fucking name.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:53.75,2:11:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你做得对  -我做得对\N- You did the right thing. - I did the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:55.55,2:11:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做得很对\NYou did the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:56.63,2:11:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我每天都要跟那个\NI sat there every day with that
Dialogue: 0,2:11:58.55,2:12:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱发牢骚的新泽西狗杂种坐在一起\Nwhining cocksucker from New Jersey,
Dialogue: 0,2:12:02.00,2:12:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听他说有他多么不幸  有多困难\Ntalking to me about his woes, his problems,
Dialogue: 0,2:12:06.21,2:12:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我只是想安安静静地吃个冰淇淋\Nand all I wanted to do was finish my ice cream in peace.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:10.42,2:12:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个狗杂种开会迟到了十五分钟\NThis cocksucker shows up at a meeting 15 minutes late,
Dialogue: 0,2:12:15.67,2:12:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还穿着他妈的短裤\Nwearing fucking shorts!
Dialogue: 0,2:12:18.38,2:12:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-谁会穿短裤去开会  -谁都不会\N- Who wears shorts to a meeting? - Nobody.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:20.92,2:12:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-没错  -没人会这么做\N- That's right. - Nobody.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:23.34,2:12:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还说我没有表示感激\NI'm not showing appreciation?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:25.09,2:12:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我说的\NIt's not me.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:26.63,2:12:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是有人这么说\NAccording to some people...
Dialogue: 0,2:12:27.71,2:12:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道不是你  是另有他人\NNo, I know it's not you. Some people...
Dialogue: 0,2:12:30.50,2:12:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另有他人说我没有表示感激\NSome people say I'm not showing appreciation?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:32.92,2:12:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就去他们的吧\NWell, then fuck them.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:35.13,2:12:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这是在帮你  吉米\NI'm trying to help you, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:36.67,2:12:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\NI know you are.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:38.46,2:12:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是谁都别想威胁霍法\NBut nobody threatens Hoffa.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:40.25,2:12:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? 就是现在 ?\N? The time is now ?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:42.59,2:12:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? 就是当下 ?\N? The time is now ?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:44.96,2:12:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? 就是此刻 ?\N? The time is now ?
Dialogue: 0,2:13:02.55,2:13:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他当过司机\NHe has done it as a driver,
Dialogue: 0,2:13:04.55,2:13:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当过工会组织者\Nhe has done it as an organizer,
Dialogue: 0,2:13:07.00,2:13:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有可能在场的大多数来宾都不知道\Nand I don't think many of you here know this,
Dialogue: 0,2:13:09.84,2:13:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗兰克手握一项记录\Nbut Frank holds a record.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:13.30,2:13:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在罢工纠察线上被逮捕次数最多的人\NIt's most arrests on the picket line.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:18.59,2:13:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一天内26次\NTwenty-six times in 24 hours,
Dialogue: 0,2:13:23.04,2:13:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打破了我的记录\Nbeating my record.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:27.25,2:13:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错  女士们先生们  我没有夸大其词\NThere it is, ladies and gentlemen. There's no exaggeration.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:31.88,2:13:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是彻头彻尾的工会人\NHe is a union man to his bones.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:36.46,2:13:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们选择站在哪一边\NWhich side are you on?
Dialogue: 0,2:13:38.25,2:13:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这边\NYour side!
Dialogue: 0,2:13:39.63,2:13:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪一边\NWhose side?
Dialogue: 0,2:13:40.71,2:13:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这边\NYour side!
Dialogue: 0,2:13:41.92,2:13:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这边\NMy side.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:42.75,2:13:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这边\NYour side.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:43.88,2:13:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他那边  -没错\N- His side. - Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,2:13:46.00,2:13:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样\NThere it is.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:47.67,2:13:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以今晚我很荣幸在这里\NAnd so, it is an honor for me to be here tonight
Dialogue: 0,2:13:51.67,2:13:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将这份奖\Nto present this award
Dialogue: 0,2:13:53.34,2:13:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,颁给我亲爱的朋友  弗兰克・希兰先生\Nto my dear friend, Mr. Frank Sheeran!
Dialogue: 0,2:14:07.13,2:14:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  吉米  非常感谢\NThank you, Jimmy, thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:10.30,2:14:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也谢谢我亲爱的妻子琳妮\NAnd thank you to my lovely wife Reenie
Dialogue: 0,2:14:13.30,2:14:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陪我来这里\Nfor being here with me.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:15.59,2:14:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感谢我甜美可爱的女儿们\NMy lovely, sweet, adorable daughters,
Dialogue: 0,2:14:18.21,2:14:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽安  多洛莉丝  康妮  佩琪\NMaryanne, Dolores, Connie, Peggy,
Dialogue: 0,2:14:22.42,2:14:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么多年一直容忍我\Nfor putting up with me for all these years.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:26.80,2:14:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有吉米  我无法表达你给我颁发这份荣誉\NAnd, Jimmy, I can't tell you what this means to me
Dialogue: 0,2:14:29.50,2:14:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我意义多么重大\Nto get this honor from you.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:31.92,2:14:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我人生最重要的时刻  非常非常感谢你\NIt's the highlight of my life. Thank you very, very much.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:35.46,2:14:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个人  詹姆斯・里德尔・霍法\NAnd this man, James Riddell Hoffa,
Dialogue: 0,2:14:39.09,2:14:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是最能成事的人\Nis the guy that gets the job done.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:44.00,2:14:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就在你身后  吉米\NI'm behind you, Jimmy.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:45.67,2:14:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一路随行\NAll the way.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:48.71,2:14:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之\NIn any case,
Dialogue: 0,2:14:49.75,2:14:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我衷心感谢你们所有人\Nfrom the deepest part of my heart, I thank you all.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:52.30,2:14:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我并不该获得这一切\N'Cause I don't really deserve all this.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:55.17,2:14:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我得了滑囊炎  我也不该得那个\NBut I have bursitis and I don't deserve that either.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:59.67,2:15:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚感谢你们所有人  感谢前来\NThank you all tonight and thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:02.34,2:15:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安\NGood night.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:14.55,2:15:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么不喊"说茄子"\NWhat happened to "Say cheese"?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:16.88,2:15:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茄子\NCheese!
Dialogue: 0,2:15:22.30,2:15:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? 让我的爱盈满你的心 ?\N? Bringing you all the love your heart can hold ?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:31.17,2:15:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? 请说"我愿意" ?\N? Please say "sí, sí" ?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:40.21,2:15:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? 说你及你那西班牙眼眸会为我等待 ?\N? Say you and your Spanish eyes will wait for me ?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:50.67,2:15:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? 蓝色的西班牙眼眸 ?\N? Blue Spanish eyes ?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:00.25,2:16:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? 墨西哥最美的双眼 ?\N? Prettiest eyes in all of Mexico ?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:09.80,2:16:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? 真诚的西班牙眼眸 ?\N? True Spanish eyes ?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:19.30,2:16:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? 请在我离开前再为我展开笑颜 ?\N? Please smile for me once more before I go... ?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:33.46,2:16:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世上只有三个人有这个\NOnly three people in the world have one of these.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:36.38,2:16:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其中只有一人是爱尔兰人\NAnd only one of them is Irish.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:38.80,2:16:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有一枚\NI have one.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:40.21,2:16:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安吉洛有一枚\NAngelo has one.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:44.17,2:16:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在你也有了\NNow you have one.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:50.09,2:16:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮\NThis is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:55.30,2:16:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道该说什么  罗素  这...\NI... I don't... I don't know what to say, Russ. It's...
Dialogue: 0,2:16:59.00,2:17:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快戴上  看看怎么样\NSlip it on. See how it looks.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:05.25,2:17:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-感觉好吗  -好\N- Feel good? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:08.88,2:17:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我让你变得多强吗  知道多强吗\NYou know how strong I made you? You know how strong?
Dialogue: 0,2:17:13.55,2:17:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的小子\NYou're my kid.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:15.88,2:17:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没人...没人能搞你\NNobody... Nobody can fuck with you.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:18.42,2:17:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没人\NNobody.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:45.67,2:17:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着  弗兰克\NListen, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:47.71,2:17:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的朋友又失控了\NThings have gotten out of hand with our friend again.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:51.75,2:17:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些人对他意见很大\NAnd some people are having serious problems with him.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:55.84,2:17:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到现在这个地步\NAnd it's at a point where
Dialogue: 0,2:17:58.80,2:18:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必须找他谈谈  告诉他\Nyou're gonna have to talk to him and tell him
Dialogue: 0,2:18:02.21,2:18:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了\Nit's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:06.38,2:18:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止\NWhat it is?
Dialogue: 0,2:18:07.59,2:18:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  这是他们的意愿\NYes. It's what they want.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:10.09,2:18:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经到这步了\NIt's where it's gotten.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:13.09,2:18:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和他亲近  或许他会听你的\NYou're close to him. Maybe he'll listen to you.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:15.80,2:18:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我和他谈过\NYou know I talked to him.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:17.21,2:18:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他这人很固执  你了解他的\NHe's a tough guy to talk to. You know him.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:19.21,2:18:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他没得选\NHe has no choice.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:21.05,2:18:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他没得选\NHe has no choice.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:23.25,2:18:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些是大人物\NThese are the higher-ups.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:26.71,2:18:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也是个大人物  不是吗\NWell, he's a higher-up too. I mean... No?
Dialogue: 0,2:18:30.05,2:18:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和他们不同  你知道的\NNot like this. You know that.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:32.30,2:18:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  弗兰克\NCome on now, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:36.67,2:18:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他们能干掉一个总统\NIf they can whack a president,
Dialogue: 0,2:18:38.80,2:18:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们就能干掉一个工会主席\Nthey can whack a president of the union.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:42.67,2:18:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道  我也知道\NYou know it and I know it.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:55.55,2:18:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和他谈过一次又一次\NI talk to this guy, I talk to him, I talk to him,
Dialogue: 0,2:18:57.46,2:18:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是不听\NI talk to him, he don't listen.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:58.84,2:19:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他现在必须听  我得让他听进去\NBut he's gotta listen now. I gotta make him listen.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:03.67,2:19:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样不对  他就是个傻瓜\NThat ain't right. He's... he's a fucking knucklehead.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:17.96,2:19:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米  我和罗素谈了\NJimmy. I talked to Russ.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:20.67,2:19:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他和托尼谈过\NHe talked to Tony.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:21.96,2:19:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说的话是认真的\NHe means what he's saying.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:24.17,2:19:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-谁  罗素吗  -不  托尼\N- Who? Russ? - No, Tony.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:26.38,2:19:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-托尼  -是的\N- Tony? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:28.17,2:19:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说的话也是认真的\NWell, I mean what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:30.59,2:19:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他那该死的西西里肥脑袋似乎就是不明白\NHe can't seem to get that through his fat, fucking Sicilian head.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:34.42,2:19:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不对  别担心\NCan he? Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:36.38,2:19:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了\NWhat's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,2:19:37.63,2:19:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看起来...\NYou... you look...
Dialogue: 0,2:19:38.84,2:19:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我很担心  -我知道\N- I'm concerned. - Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:40.00,2:19:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看起来就在担心  你担心什么\NYou look concerned. What are you concerned about?
Dialogue: 0,2:19:42.55,2:19:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...\NI'm... I'm...
Dialogue: 0,2:19:43.17,2:19:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该担心的是他们\NThey should be concerned.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:44.75,2:19:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他们确实担心  -那就让他们担心去\N- They are. They are. - Well, let them be.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:46.09,2:19:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们不止有一点点担心\NThey're more than a little concerned.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:47.67,2:19:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们担心颇多\NThere's widespread concern.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:49.09,2:19:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是个大问题\NIt's a big problem.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:52.13,2:19:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托尼让老爷子叫我告诉你...\NTony told the old man to tell me to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,2:19:56.50,2:19:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"到此为止了"\N"It's what it is."
Dialogue: 0,2:20:01.96,2:20:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止\NWhat it is?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:02.84,2:20:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了\NIt's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:08.05,2:20:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  听我说\NPlease, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:11.50,2:20:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们不敢\NThey wouldn't dare.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:13.42,2:20:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-别...  -他们不敢\N- Don't... - They wouldn't dare.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:15.25,2:20:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-吉米  -得了吧  弗兰克\N- Jimmy... - Please, Frank, come on.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:17.09,2:20:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-别说他们不敢  -不\N- Don't say they wouldn't dare. - No.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:18.88,2:20:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别跟我说这种话...都是胡扯\NDon't... don't tell me that kinda... That's fairy tales.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:21.92,2:20:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别说他们不敢\NNo, don't say they wouldn't dare.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:24.50,2:20:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我出了什么事\NIf something funny happens to me...
Dialogue: 0,2:20:29.09,2:20:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们就完了\Nthey're done.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:29.96,2:20:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明白吗  他们也清楚这点\NYou understand that? And they know it.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:32.09,2:20:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我有文件  我有证据\NBecause I got files. I got proof.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:34.80,2:20:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有记录  我有录音带\NI got records. I got tapes.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:36.55,2:20:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我想  他们随时会完蛋\NAny time I want, they'll be gone.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:39.00,2:20:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些几内亚混蛋\NThese Guinea motherfuckers
Dialogue: 0,2:20:40.63,2:20:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,余生都会在监狱度过\Nwill spend the rest of their lives in jail,
Dialogue: 0,2:20:42.80,2:20:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们清楚\Nand they know it.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:45.25,2:20:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们清楚\NThey know it.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:45.84,2:20:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你现在说的正是他们担心的\NBut what you're saying is what they're concerned about.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:48.21,2:20:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在说的是我知道他们的事\NWhat I'm saying is I know things.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:49.92,2:20:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道他们不知道我知道的事\NI know things they don't know I know.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:53.71,2:20:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-拜托  -你真的要冒那个险吗\N- Please... - Are you gonna take that chance?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:56.00,2:20:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我冒什么...我为什么要冒险\NWhat chance am I... Why should I be taking a chance?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:58.00,2:20:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们说到此为止了\NThey're saying this is it.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:00.34,2:21:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们说到此为止  那就到此为止吗\NThey're saying this is it, and then it's it?
Dialogue: 0,2:21:02.34,2:21:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-胡说  胡说  弗兰克  -别这样\N- Bullshit. Bullshit, Frank. - Come on.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:04.46,2:21:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米  我是想告诉你\NJimmy, I'm trying to tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:06.00,2:21:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你是  你在告诉我他们威胁我\NI know you are. You're telling me that they're threatening me
Dialogue: 0,2:21:08.25,2:21:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必须照他们说的做\Nand I gotta do what they say.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:09.88,2:21:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不只是威胁  那是底线\NIt's more than a threat. It's the bottom line.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:12.71,2:21:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,底线\NThe bottom line.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:14.55,2:21:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了\NIt's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:15.92,2:21:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们搞我  我就搞他们\NThey do something to me, I do something to them.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:19.46,2:21:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道这个  别的我不知道  你知道吗\NThat's all I know. I don't know anything else. Do you?
Dialogue: 0,2:21:24.34,2:21:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我要怎么做  我该怎么跟麦基说\NSo what am I gonna do? What am I gonna tell McGee?
Dialogue: 0,2:21:27.34,2:21:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说你不肯听吗\NThat you're not gonna listen?
Dialogue: 0,2:21:29.05,2:21:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不习惯有人不听他的\NHe ain't used to people not listening to him.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:30.38,2:21:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是\NWell, neither am I.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:32.88,2:21:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-什么  -我也是\N- What? - Neither am I.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:35.75,2:21:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我不知道该怎么办了\NThen I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:36.67,2:21:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许你该找些保镖\NI mean, maybe you should get some bodies around you
Dialogue: 0,2:21:38.42,2:21:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-保护你  -得了吧\N- for protection. - Come on. Please.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:40.34,2:21:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会选那条路\NI'm not gonna go that route.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:42.05,2:21:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这么对我  弗兰克\NDon't do this to me, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:43.71,2:21:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说"找些保镖"是什么意思  我不需要\NWhat do you mean, "bodies around me"? I don't need...
Dialogue: 0,2:21:46.13,2:21:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你找保镖  他们就会找上你的家人\NYou put bodies around you, then they go after your family.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:48.71,2:21:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-这不重要  你担心吗  -我担心\N- It doesn't matter. You worried? - I'm worried.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:50.96,2:21:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去找些保镖吧  我告诉你为什么\NGet some bodies around you. I'll tell you why.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:54.55,2:21:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这事可能落到你身上\NThis could happen to you.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:56.13,2:21:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们可能找上你\NThey could come after you
Dialogue: 0,2:21:58.42,2:21:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你支持我\Nsince you're with me.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:00.25,2:22:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗\NNo?
Dialogue: 0,2:22:03.63,2:22:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很担心\NI'm worried.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:04.96,2:22:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉罗素我对他只有尊重\NTell Russ I got nothing but respect for him.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:07.67,2:22:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和他有点小摩擦\NI got a little trouble with him.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:10.21,2:22:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们之前谈的时候  我有点失控\NWe were talking before and I just got a little crazy.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:12.50,2:22:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你知道我什么样  有时会发脾气  -是的\N- You know how I am. I just blow. Sometimes. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:15.59,2:22:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,气得扭头就走\NI just walked away like that.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:17.00,2:22:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我就是这样的人\NBut I get that way. I get abrupt.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:19.00,2:22:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许你能告诉他我多么尊重他\NMaybe you could tell him how much I respect him.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:22.42,2:22:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对他只有尊重\NI have nothing but respect for this guy.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:24.88,2:22:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我永远不会伤害他\NI would never hurt him,
Dialogue: 0,2:22:26.59,2:22:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管我手上有什么文件  不管我做什么\Nno matter what I do with files, or whatever I do with anything.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:29.84,2:22:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该亲自告诉他\NBut you should tell him. Yourself.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:31.96,2:22:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我不要亲自告诉他\NNo, I'm not gonna tell him myself.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:33.21,2:22:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-拜托  -算了吧\N- Please. - Come on.
