Dialogue: 0,2:31:13.48,2:31:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,够了  谢谢\NThat's good, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:21.65,2:31:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们今天要去一趟克林顿港\NWe're gonna take a ride up to Port Clinton today.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:29.77,2:31:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为我们要待在这里\NI thought we were staying here.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:32.47,2:31:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  夫人们待在这里\NNo, the girls are gonna stay here.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:35.07,2:31:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们俩去\NYou and me, we're going up and, uh...
Dialogue: 0,2:31:38.50,2:31:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最多三个小时就会回来\Nwe'll be back three hours tops.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:44.08,2:31:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去克林顿港干什么\NBut... But what's in Port Clinton?
Dialogue: 0,2:31:47.22,2:31:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐飞机\NA plane.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:51.86,2:31:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐飞机  去哪里\NA plane? To where?
Dialogue: 0,2:31:54.16,2:31:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,底特律\NDetroit.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:02.88,2:32:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在要去底特律吗\NWe're going to Detroit now?
Dialogue: 0,2:32:05.05,2:32:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  你要去底特律\NNo, you're gonna go to Detroit.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:10.05,2:32:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回来之后\NAnd when you come back,
Dialogue: 0,2:32:11.95,2:32:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们带上夫人们\Nme and you, we get together with the girls,
Dialogue: 0,2:32:14.82,2:32:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,优哉游哉地上路\Nwe take a nice slow drive up.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:17.68,2:32:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时不时停下来抽根烟\NWith cigarette breaks, you know.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:31.05,2:32:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗兰克\NFrank.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:32.85,2:32:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必须让你去做这件事\NI had to put you into this thing,
Dialogue: 0,2:32:35.72,2:32:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否则你绝不会袖手旁观\Nor you would never let it happen.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:38.73,2:32:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你不会\NAnd I know you wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:45.76,2:32:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但事已至此\NBut it's gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:49.87,2:32:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样  都得解决他\NEither way, he's going.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:58.96,2:33:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白你的感受  弗兰克  相信我\NI know how you feel, Frank. Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:01.61,2:33:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白你的感受\NI know how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:04.86,2:33:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我之前跟你说过  我们已经尽力帮他了\NI told you before, we tried everything to help him.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:07.58,2:33:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的\NYou know that.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:08.73,2:33:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你尽力了\NYou tried.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:12.71,2:33:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是他自找的\NHe brought this on himself.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:16.62,2:33:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还牵扯到了我们\NAnd it's landing on us.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:22.35,2:33:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们同意这样安排\NThe only reason they agreed to this
Dialogue: 0,2:33:25.22,2:33:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是出于对我的尊重\Nwas out of respect to me.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:29.78,2:33:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和琳妮不会有事的\NBut you and Reenie will be okay,
Dialogue: 0,2:33:32.36,2:33:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是我的人\N'cause you're with me.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:38.82,2:33:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的人\NYou're with me.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:19.30,2:34:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你的眼镜给我\NGive me your glasses.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:21.06,2:36:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯撒路83号
Dialogue: 0,2:36:41.60,2:36:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,红狐餐厅
Dialogue: 0,2:37:25.38,2:37:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯撒路83号
Dialogue: 0,2:38:48.03,2:38:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗兰克\NHey, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:49.93,2:38:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小萨\NHey, Sal.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:53.44,2:38:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,查奇迟到了\NChuckie's late.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:48.66,2:39:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他吗\NThat him?
Dialogue: 0,2:39:54.41,2:39:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:57.78,2:39:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天呐\NJesus.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:03.52,2:40:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是萨利\NI'm Sally.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:05.15,2:40:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好\NHi.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:08.12,2:40:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-小查  -弗兰克\N- Chuck. - Frank.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:09.82,2:40:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走  我不想你爸因为迟到对我大吼大叫\NLet's go. I don't want your father yelling at me for being late.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:11.89,2:40:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗兰克  你坐前面\NFrank, you take the front.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:14.62,2:40:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-这他妈怎么回事  -怎么了\N- What the fuck is this? - What?
Dialogue: 0,2:40:17.04,2:40:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湿漉漉的\NIt's wet.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:18.48,2:40:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我刚给朋友送了一条冻鱼\NYeah, I had a frozen fish I had to deliver for a friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:23.51,2:40:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一条鱼\NA fish?
Dialogue: 0,2:40:24.98,2:40:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,座位是被鱼给弄湿了吗\NThe seat is wet from a fish?
Dialogue: 0,2:40:26.07,2:40:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对  你现在想让我怎么办\NYeah, I know. What do you want me to do about it now?
Dialogue: 0,2:40:27.69,2:40:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-老天啊  -我坐后面吧\N- Jesus Christ. - I'll sit back there.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:28.93,2:40:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  没关系  你坐前面\NNo, no, no, it's all right. You sit in the front.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:30.26,2:40:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我坐后面\NI'll sit there.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:32.05,2:40:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我坐后面  你坐前面\NI'll sit here, you take the front.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:33.41,2:40:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  不\NNo, no.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:34.57,2:40:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我坐后面\NI'll sit there.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:39.00,2:40:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我不要坐前面  -你怎么就不...\N- I'm not sitting there. - Why don't you...
Dialogue: 0,2:40:39.96,2:40:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要坐后面\NI'm sitting there.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:43.58,2:40:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  随你便\NAll right, sit where you want.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:47.17,2:40:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要给你拿张报纸吗  弗兰克\NYou want me to get you a newspaper, Frank?
Dialogue: 0,2:40:48.89,2:40:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  走吧  我们得快点\NIt's okay. Let's go. We gotta hurry.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:04.78,2:41:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什么鱼\NWhat kind of fish?
Dialogue: 0,2:41:08.14,2:41:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,2:41:11.46,2:41:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你送的是什么鱼\NWhat kind of fish?
Dialogue: 0,2:41:14.79,2:41:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  就是可以吃的鱼\NI don't know. The kind you eat. A fish.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:18.82,2:41:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道是哪种鱼吗\NYou don't know what kind?
Dialogue: 0,2:41:22.12,2:41:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道\NNo. I don't.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:24.70,2:41:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你从哪弄来的\NWhere did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,2:41:27.02,2:41:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说呢  卖鱼的地方\NWhat the fuck. At a fish place.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:31.19,2:41:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就直接过去说"给我条鱼"吗\NWhat, you just go in there and say, "Gimme a fish"?
Dialogue: 0,2:41:35.73,2:41:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多吧\NPretty much. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:38.69,2:41:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没说你要鲑鱼\NYou didn't say you want a salmon,
Dialogue: 0,2:41:40.26,2:41:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是黑线鳕\Nyou want a... haddock,
Dialogue: 0,2:41:42.13,2:41:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是鳕鱼吗\Nyou want a... a fucking cod?
Dialogue: 0,2:41:44.44,2:41:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是哪种鱼有什么关系吗\NWhat the fuck does it matter what kind of fish it was?
Dialogue: 0,2:41:47.96,2:41:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么那么关心那条鱼\NWhy are you so concerned about this fish?
Dialogue: 0,2:41:49.45,2:41:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想搞清楚...\NI'm just trying to understand how...
Dialogue: 0,2:41:50.93,2:41:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这...\NDoes it...
Dialogue: 0,2:41:54.23,2:41:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能买到一条鱼  却不知道是什么鱼\N...how a person can buy a fish and not know what kind it was.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:59.31,2:42:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那条鱼就在那里等着我\NThere was a fish waiting for me there.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:04.97,2:42:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没问那是什么鱼  抱歉\NI didn't ask what kind of fish it was. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:11.80,2:42:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-就是说你朋友已经把鱼订好了  -对\N- So your friend had already ordered this fish. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:20.94,2:42:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是有人问起  我得能解释明白\N'Cause I wanna be able to explain this if somebody asks me.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:28.39,2:42:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,红狐餐厅
Dialogue: 0,2:42:31.08,2:42:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  没问题\NYeah. Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:45.30,2:42:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸\NDad.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:48.01,2:42:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,查奇\NChuckie.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:49.04,2:42:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-抱歉我迟到了  我得去送...  -迟到\N- Yeah, sorry I'm late. I had to drop off... - Late?
Dialogue: 0,2:42:51.67,2:42:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你来这里干什么\NWhat the fuck are you even doing here?
Dialogue: 0,2:42:53.46,2:42:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-谁让你来的  -吉米\N- Who invited you? - Hey, Jimmy.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:58.06,2:42:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁\NWho the fuck are you?
Dialogue: 0,2:42:59.77,2:43:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是普罗的人\NI'm with Pro.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:01.24,2:43:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是普罗的人\NYou're with Pro?
Dialogue: 0,2:43:02.77,2:43:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是那个放我鸽子的龟孙的人\NAre you with the cocksucker who just stood me up?
Dialogue: 0,2:43:05.20,2:43:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会等人超过十分钟\NI don't wait for anybody more than ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:07.36,2:43:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在房子里\NHe's at the house.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:09.30,2:43:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么房子\NWhat house?
Dialogue: 0,2:43:10.34,2:43:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和罗素在一起\NWith Russ.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:12.52,2:43:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-罗素  搞什么  -看看谁在后面\N- Russ? What the fuck is... - Hey, look who's here.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:15.44,2:43:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-弗兰克  -吉米\N- Frank. - Jimmy.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:17.09,2:43:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事\NWhat the fuck is going on?
Dialogue: 0,2:43:19.51,2:43:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等你  我两点就到了\NI was waiting for you. I was there at two o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:21.71,2:43:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该到场的  出什么事了\NYou were supposed to show. What happened?
Dialogue: 0,2:43:22.75,2:43:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  但麦基来了  他决定过来\NI'm sorry. But McGee's here, he decided to come.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:25.89,2:43:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他不喜欢这里  他不想来这里\NBut he ain't comfortable here. He don't wanna come here.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:28.33,2:43:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在房子里\NHe's at the house.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:29.15,2:43:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-麦基来底特律了  -对  他来了\N- McGee's in Detroit? - Yeah, he's here.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:31.81,2:43:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他决定过来\NHe decided to come.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:35.49,2:43:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是来帮忙理清这件事的\NYeah, he came to help straighten this all out.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:39.03,2:43:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,房子\NThe house?
Dialogue: 0,2:43:45.88,2:43:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事后我们会带你来取车的\NWe'll bring you back after to get your car.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:53.81,2:43:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:56.50,2:43:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:02.53,2:44:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好  -嗯\N- Yeah. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:09.88,2:44:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,红狐餐厅
Dialogue: 0,2:44:14.07,2:44:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前车里放了条鱼\NThere was a fish in here,
Dialogue: 0,2:44:14.97,2:44:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们已经清理干净了\Nbut we cleaned it up.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:17.66,2:44:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鱼\NA fish?
Dialogue: 0,2:44:19.98,2:44:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,查奇在车里放了条鱼\NChuckie had a fucking fish in here.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:21.78,2:44:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他连是什么鱼都不知道\NDidn't even know what kind.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:22.74,2:44:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但现在没事了  我擦干净了\NBut it's okay now. I wiped it up.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:24.82,2:44:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我在座位上垫了块手帕  -我闻出来了\N- I got the handkerchief here. - Yeah, I can smell it.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:28.10,2:44:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,查奇\NHey, Chuckie.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:28.60,2:44:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在车里放了条鱼吗\NYou had a fish in here in your car?
Dialogue: 0,2:44:30.69,2:44:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给鲍比・霍姆斯的\NFor Bobby Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:32.28,2:44:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的  鲍比喜欢吃鱼\NYou know, Bobby likes fish.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:34.11,2:44:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们清理干净了  吉米  没关系\NWe cleaned it up, Jimmy. It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:35.85,2:44:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你清理干净了\NYou cleaned it up?
Dialogue: 0,2:44:37.42,2:44:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你清理干净了  -是的\N- You cleaned it up? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:39.20,2:44:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你他妈了解鱼吗\NWhat the fuck you know about fish?
Dialogue: 0,2:44:41.28,2:44:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这辈子有抓过鱼吗\NYou ever caught a fucking fish in your life?
Dialogue: 0,2:44:44.28,2:44:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:45.11,2:44:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你就不了解  对吧\NWell, then you don't know. See?
Dialogue: 0,2:44:47.49,2:44:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小查\NChuck.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:48.05,2:44:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听我说  永远不要在车里放鱼\NListen to me. Never put a fish in your car.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:51.02,2:44:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,味道是散不掉的\NYou never get the smell out.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:52.74,2:44:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-嗯...  -除非包装得很好\N- No... - Unless you pack it tight, you know.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:54.56,2:44:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道\NNo, I... I know.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:56.00,2:44:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你知道吗  记住了  -对\N- You know? Remember that. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:57.98,2:44:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:58.79,2:45:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会受益匪浅的\NIt'll help you in life.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:05.48,2:45:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗兰克  你就不能两点来找我  告诉我这事吗\NFrank, you couldn't come by at 2:00 and tell me this?
Dialogue: 0,2:45:08.45,2:45:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我傻傻地在那等了你四十分钟\NI was waiting there 40 minutes like a fuckin' moron.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:11.44,2:45:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米  抱歉  我刚到就赶过来了\NJimmy, I'm sorry. I came as soon as I got here.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:13.98,2:45:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你今天早上到的  -不是\N- You got in this morning. - No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:15.89,2:45:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天下午才到的\NI got here this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:17.09,2:45:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗素在克林顿港办事  我得等他\NRussell had business in Port Clinton. I had to wait for him.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:19.98,2:45:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他提醒了我  我忘记了\NHe reminded me. I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:21.60,2:45:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们马上赶来  我刚到\NSo, we had to come and as soon as we got here,
Dialogue: 0,2:45:23.75,2:45:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就直接过来找你了\NI came right here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:25.38,2:45:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有对罗素不敬的意思\NAll due respect to Russ, you know,
Dialogue: 0,2:45:28.61,2:45:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但应该让人提前告诉我的\Nbut somebody should have come tell me, you know.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:31.53,2:45:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最起码应该来告诉我时间推迟了\NJust come tell me it's 2:30, 2:40, at the very least.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:34.95,2:45:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说得对  我是说...\NYou're not incorrect. I mean...
Dialogue: 0,2:45:36.61,2:45:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,普罗算哪根葱  还派个狗腿子过来\NWho the fuck is Pro? He sends a fucking errand boy here.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:40.73,2:45:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不会待太久\NHe ain't stayin'.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:41.86,2:45:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道他不会待太久\NI know he ain't staying.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:42.99,2:45:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关键不在于他待多久\NThat's not the point, he's staying or not staying.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:45.09,2:45:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关键在于普罗派他过来\NThe point is Pro sent him.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:46.93,2:45:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗\NYou know?
Dialogue: 0,2:45:47.77,2:45:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关键是他应该亲自来接我\NPoint is, he should've come picked me up himself.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:49.55,2:45:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这才是问题的关键\NThat's the point I'm makin'.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:54.36,2:45:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你戴着这副眼镜能看得清吗\NCan you even see out of those glasses?
Dialogue: 0,2:45:57.56,2:45:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都看不清\NI can't see a fucking thing.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:59.45,2:46:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好  幸好不是你开车\NThat's good. I'm glad you're not driving, then.
Dialogue: 0,2:46:10.61,2:46:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在这...这边\NYeah, it's right... It's right up...
Dialogue: 0,2:46:12.69,2:46:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在这边  这边\NIt's right up here. Right... Right up...
Dialogue: 0,2:46:14.73,2:46:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有楼梯的那房子\NThat building with the staircase.
Dialogue: 0,2:46:18.22,2:46:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你带家伙了吗\NYou got your friend with you?
Dialogue: 0,2:46:19.87,2:46:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-带了  -很好\N- Right here. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,2:46:22.23,2:46:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道这个龟孙会做出什么事\NYou never know with this cocksucker,
Dialogue: 0,2:46:24.18,2:46:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管罗素在不在场\Nwith or without Russ there.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:05.40,2:47:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走  弗兰克  快\NLet's get outta here, Frank. Come on.
