Dialogue: 0,2:48:30.72,2:48:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In The Still Of The Night - The Five Satins
Dialogue: 0,2:48:36.83,2:48:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? Hold me again ?
Dialogue: 0,2:48:39.87,2:48:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? With all of your might ?
