Dialogue: 0,2:48:45.85,2:48:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? In the still of the night ?
Dialogue: 0,2:49:23.17,2:49:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? So before the light ?
Dialogue: 0,2:49:29.63,2:49:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? Hold me again ?
Dialogue: 0,2:49:32.75,2:49:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,? With all of your might ?
