Dialogue: 0,2:49:42.86,2:49:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡车司机工会前主席詹姆斯・霍法\NJames Hoffa, former president of the Teamsters Union,
Dialogue: 0,2:49:45.46,2:49:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,于周三失踪\Ndisappeared on Wednesday.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:46.81,2:49:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,截至今晚  尚未发现他的踪迹\NAnd as of tonight, no trace of him has been found.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:50.12,2:49:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霍法在监狱服刑四年  他坦承\NHoffa spent four years in prison and made no bones
Dialogue: 0,2:49:52.90,2:49:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-自己打算...  -弗兰克\N- about his intention... - Frank.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:54.33,2:49:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从他的继任弗兰克・菲茨西蒙斯手上\N...to get the presidency back from his successor,
Dialogue: 0,2:49:56.55,2:49:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夺回主席之位\NFrank Fitzsimmons.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:57.81,2:49:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲茨西蒙斯的儿子是副主席...\NFitzsimmons' son is the vice president of...
Dialogue: 0,2:49:59.85,2:50:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没消息吗\NStill nothing?
Dialogue: 0,2:50:02.28,2:50:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小菲茨西蒙斯的车被炸了  他当时不在车内\N...young Fitzsimmons' car was bombed. He was not in it.
Dialogue: 0,2:50:05.29,2:50:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但底特律地方工会内确有不和\NBut there is bad blood in the Detroit Local.
Dialogue: 0,2:50:08.69,2:50:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霍法于周三下午失踪\NHoffa disappeared Wednesday afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,2:50:11.64,2:50:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前已过去48个小时  仍然不清楚\NNow, more than 48 hours later, with no word yet
Dialogue: 0,2:50:14.97,2:50:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霍法出了什么事  警方对此极为关切\Non what happened to Hoffa, police are extremely concerned.
Dialogue: 0,2:50:18.97,2:50:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当局急于弄清楚\NAuthorities are most anxious to find whom
Dialogue: 0,2:50:21.27,2:50:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霍法在红狐餐厅外见的是谁\NHoffa was supposed to meet outside the Red Fox restaurant
Dialogue: 0,2:50:24.51,2:50:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是最后有人看到他的地方\Nwhere he was last seen.
Dialogue: 0,2:50:26.73,2:50:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警方认为可能是安东尼・加卡罗内\NPolice think it could have been a man named Anthony Giacalone,
Dialogue: 0,2:50:30.33,2:50:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他被称为底特律黑手党的大佬\Ndescribed as a big man in the Detroit Mafia.
Dialogue: 0,2:50:32.99,2:50:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霍法的儿子詹姆斯今天试图联系加卡罗内\NHoffa's son, James, tried to contact Giacalone today,
Dialogue: 0,2:50:36.37,2:50:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但没能联系上\Nbut didn't succeed.
Dialogue: 0,2:50:37.70,2:50:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霍法的亲朋好友今天留在\NHoffa's family and friends stayed
Dialogue: 0,2:50:39.84,2:50:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,位于湖口镇的家中\Nin the family home in Lake Orion today...
Dialogue: 0,2:50:41.88,2:50:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我应该打给约\NI should call Jo.
Dialogue: 0,2:50:45.40,2:50:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还没有打给约吗\NYou haven't called Jo yet?
Dialogue: 0,2:50:54.12,2:50:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,2:50:55.61,2:50:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,2:50:57.70,2:50:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,2:51:00.25,2:51:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么为什么\NWhy what?
Dialogue: 0,2:51:03.32,2:51:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么还没有打给约\NWhy haven't you called Jo?
Dialogue: 0,2:51:05.47,2:51:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人索要赎金之类的吗\NHas anybody come forward with a ransom demand or anything like that?
Dialogue: 0,2:51:08.95,2:51:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前还没有\NNot as of yet.
Dialogue: 0,2:51:10.23,2:51:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认为这起绑架是为了索要赎金吗\NDo you think the abduction was for ransom?
Dialogue: 0,2:51:13.34,2:51:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在打给她\NI'm gonna call her now.
Dialogue: 0,2:51:16.26,2:51:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认为这起绑架\NDo you think the abduction
Dialogue: 0,2:51:17.26,2:51:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和他所在的299号地方工会\Nhad anything to do with the recent conflicts
Dialogue: 0,2:51:20.42,2:51:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近的内部冲突有关吗\Nwithin Local 299, his own Local?
Dialogue: 0,2:51:22.38,2:51:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为工会政治\NI think the union politics
Dialogue: 0,2:51:24.85,2:51:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然是需要进行调查的\Nis certainly something that has to be investigated.
Dialogue: 0,2:51:26.77,2:51:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,国际卡车司机工会的一位高层人士\NOne high official of the Teamsters International
Dialogue: 0,2:51:29.31,2:51:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,声称他担心发生了最坏的事\Nsays he fears the worst,
Dialogue: 0,2:51:31.10,2:51:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即霍法可能已经被杀\Nthat Hoffa may have been killed.
Dialogue: 0,2:51:33.94,2:51:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全国广播公司新闻频道的罗伯特・哈格\NRobert Hager, NBC News,
Dialogue: 0,2:51:35.74,2:51:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在密歇根州布隆菲尔德为您报道\NBloomfield, Michigan.
Dialogue: 0,2:51:38.69,2:51:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,底特律外的一处卡车休息站\NAt a truck stop outside Detroit,
Dialogue: 0,2:51:40.62,2:51:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霍法在这升任卡车司机工会主席\Nwhere Hoffa rose to the top in the Teamsters Union,
Dialogue: 0,2:51:43.65,2:51:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站内的卡车司机们众说纷纭\Ntruck drivers had a variety of theories...
Dialogue: 0,2:51:45.98,2:51:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她自那天后就没和我说过话\NShe stopped talking to me that day.
Dialogue: 0,2:51:48.77,2:51:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1975年8月3日\NAugust 3rd, 1975.
Dialogue: 0,2:51:53.27,2:51:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她现在有份好工作  住在费城外\NShe's got a good job now and lives just outside Philly.
Dialogue: 0,2:51:58.58,2:52:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我的女儿\NBut my daughter...
Dialogue: 0,2:52:01.07,2:52:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佩琪\NPeggy...
Dialogue: 0,2:52:03.03,2:52:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自那天后\Ndisappeared...
Dialogue: 0,2:52:05.58,2:52:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就从我的生命中消失了\Nfrom my life that day.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:11.14,2:52:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:14.32,2:52:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-喂  -喂\N- Hello. - Hello?
Dialogue: 0,2:52:16.08,2:52:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约\NJo.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:17.05,2:52:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约\NJo?
Dialogue: 0,2:52:19.04,2:52:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是关于...\NIt's... It's...
Dialogue: 0,2:52:20.56,2:52:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-弗兰克  是你吗  -是我\N- Frank. Frank? - Yeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:23.93,2:52:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-嗯  -我不...\N- Yeah... - I don't...
Dialogue: 0,2:52:26.71,2:52:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-听着  我...  -弗兰克\N- Look, I... - Frank...
Dialogue: 0,2:52:29.64,2:52:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得他还活着吗\NDo you think... Do you think he's alive?
Dialogue: 0,2:52:34.87,2:52:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他肯定还活着\NHe's gotta be.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:37.46,2:52:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得乐观一点\NYou know, you gotta think positively.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:39.31,2:52:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没过很久...\NIt's just, you know, it ain't that long. It's just...
Dialogue: 0,2:52:41.53,2:52:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你...\NBut do you...
Dialogue: 0,2:52:43.23,2:52:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他现在还好吗\NDo you know he's okay?
Dialogue: 0,2:52:44.69,2:52:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  你了解我的  我...\NNo, no, no, I mean, you know me, I...
Dialogue: 0,2:52:47.40,2:52:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他可能干了"香蕉乔"那样的事\NHe maybe did something like the Joe Bananas thing,
Dialogue: 0,2:52:47.42,2:52:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美国黑手党"第一教父"\N约瑟夫・博南诺的外号
Dialogue: 0,2:52:50.19,2:52:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把自己绑架了\Nwhere, you know, he had himself kidnapped
Dialogue: 0,2:52:53.47,2:52:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后毫发无损地回来了\Nand then came back, but he wasn't hurt, nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:56.69,2:52:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许他\NMaybe he...
Dialogue: 0,2:52:58.83,2:52:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许他只是想\NMaybe he just felt, you know,
Dialogue: 0,2:52:59.91,2:53:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清理一下自己的思绪\Nhe wanted to clear his head a bit.
Dialogue: 0,2:53:01.77,2:53:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你得相信...\NBut you gotta just think that it's gonna be...
Dialogue: 0,2:53:04.71,2:53:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会有事的\NIt's gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:53:06.94,2:53:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会有事的\NIt's gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:53:10.14,2:53:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不会...\NHe's gonna be...
Dialogue: 0,2:53:13.18,2:53:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么需要的话尽管找我\NIf you need anything, I'm here for you.
Dialogue: 0,2:53:15.62,2:53:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任何事都行\NAnything. Anything.
Dialogue: 0,2:53:18.89,2:53:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以...可以再打给我吗\NCan you just... Can you call me again?
Dialogue: 0,2:53:20.80,2:53:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  我会...会打给你的\NYeah, I'll call... I'll call you.
Dialogue: 0,2:53:24.50,2:53:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  我会打给你的\NYeah, I'll... I'll call you.
Dialogue: 0,2:53:27.24,2:53:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明早打给你\NI'll check in with you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,2:53:29.22,2:53:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  明天打给我\NYes, call me tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,2:53:30.96,2:53:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  我明早打给你  好吗\NOkay. I'll call you in the morning, okay?
Dialogue: 0,2:53:33.39,2:53:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你保证吗\NPromise?
Dialogue: 0,2:53:34.41,2:53:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别担心  坚强点\NDon't worry. Be strong.
Dialogue: 0,2:53:36.32,2:53:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乐观点  好吗\NBe positive, huh?
Dialogue: 0,2:53:38.59,2:53:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  约  好了\NOkay, Jo, okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:53:41.89,2:53:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,2:53:43.21,2:53:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好  -我晚点再打给你  再见\N- Okay. - Talk to ya a little later. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,2:53:45.06,2:53:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-再见  -再见  弗兰克\N- Bye. - Goodbye, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,2:54:46.09,2:54:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么简单\NIt was no more complicated than that.
Dialogue: 0,2:54:50.86,2:54:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希兰先生\NMr. Sheeran,
Dialogue: 0,2:54:52.72,2:54:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道是否有人  是什么人\Ndo you know who, if anyone,
Dialogue: 0,2:54:55.04,2:54:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绑架了詹姆斯・霍法吗\Nwas behind the disappearance of James Hoffa?
Dialogue: 0,2:54:57.83,2:55:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟吉米有关系的人\NEverybody who ever had anything to do with Jimmy
Dialogue: 0,2:55:01.42,2:55:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都被传唤进行问询\Nwas hauled in and questioned.
Dialogue: 0,2:55:03.30,2:55:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根据律师的建议\NOn the advice of counsel,
Dialogue: 0,2:55:04.25,2:55:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恕我拒绝回答这个问题\NI respectfully decline to answer that question
Dialogue: 0,2:55:06.41,2:55:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这可能会使我负罪\Non the grounds that it might tend to incriminate me.
Dialogue: 0,2:55:08.79,2:55:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  我换个问题\NOkay, let me ask you this:
Dialogue: 0,2:55:11.08,2:55:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的笔是什么颜色\Nwhat color is my pen?
Dialogue: 0,2:55:14.95,2:55:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都行使第五修正案拒绝回答\NAnd everybody took the Fifth.
Dialogue: 0,2:55:16.16,2:55:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那种情况下  只能这么做\NI mean, in that situation, that's what you do.
Dialogue: 0,2:55:19.37,2:55:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然还能怎么做呢\NWhat else are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,2:55:20.75,2:55:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而所有人都因某件事被控告和定罪\NStill, everybody got indicted or convicted on one thing or another,
Dialogue: 0,2:55:25.33,2:55:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但不是因为那件事\Nbut not that.
Dialogue: 0,2:55:26.62,2:55:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是因为吉米\NNot about Jimmy.
Dialogue: 0,2:55:28.04,2:55:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如你所知  没有人因为这件事入狱\NNobody, as you know, even went to jail for that.
Dialogue: 0,2:55:31.00,2:55:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也没有人松口  这不常见\NAnd nobody talked, which is unusual,
Dialogue: 0,2:55:33.08,2:55:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为通常来说  三个人守不住秘密\N'cause usually, three people can keep a secret
Dialogue: 0,2:55:35.75,2:55:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非另外两人不在人世\Nonly when two of them are dead.
Dialogue: 0,2:55:39.62,2:55:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺・邓赞塔和马尔科・罗西\NBruno Denzetta and Marco Rossi,
Dialogue: 0,2:55:42.20,2:55:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们因敲诈一家货运公司而分别被判刑二十年\Nthey got 20 years each for shaking down a trucking company.
Dialogue: 0,2:55:46.79,2:55:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,普罗和他们一起被判刑\NPro was convicted with them,
Dialogue: 0,2:55:48.37,2:55:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他早就因为\Nbut he was already back in school
Dialogue: 0,2:55:50.04,2:55:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我之前说过的另一件事进了监狱\Nfor that other matter I talked about before.
Dialogue: 0,2:55:52.62,2:55:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还记得可怜的工会财务\NWell, you remember that poor union treasurer,
Dialogue: 0,2:55:54.45,2:55:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"三指"托尼吗  就是比普罗获得更多选票的那个\NTony "Three Fingers," who got more votes than Pro?
Dialogue: 0,2:55:57.41,2:55:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们因此把他做掉了\NThey got him on that.
Dialogue: 0,2:55:58.91,2:56:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小虫萨利动的手\NSally Bugs, you know, he did that one.
Dialogue: 0,2:56:08.16,2:56:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一天  有人看见小虫走进了政府大楼\NOne day, Bugs was seen walking into the Federal building.
Dialogue: 0,2:56:13.00,2:56:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他做的事不是犯罪\NWhat he did itself ain't no crime.
Dialogue: 0,2:56:15.20,2:56:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多人都因为做了某事而被传唤\NI mean, a lot of people get called in for things.
Dialogue: 0,2:56:18.25,2:56:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但萨利明白事理\NBut Sally knows better.
Dialogue: 0,2:56:20.41,2:56:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么会什么都没告诉别人呢\NHow come he didn't say anything to anybody?
Dialogue: 0,2:56:23.95,2:56:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一句话都没跟别人说\NHe didn't tell anybody one word.
Dialogue: 0,2:56:26.41,2:56:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一句话都没有\NNot one word.
Dialogue: 0,2:56:28.83,2:56:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以肯定的是\NAnd one thing for sure,
Dialogue: 0,2:56:31.58,2:56:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他去那里不是为了吃午餐的\Nhe didn't go there for fucking lunch.
Dialogue: 0,2:56:46.83,2:56:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨利\NSally.
Dialogue: 0,2:56:48.62,2:56:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你好吗  -你好啊  爱尔兰人\N- What's good? - Hey, Irish.
Dialogue: 0,2:57:02.83,2:57:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后来才知道萨利确实跟别人说了\NTurns out Sally did tell somebody
Dialogue: 0,2:57:04.62,2:57:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他要去那里办事\Nhe had to go in there for something.
Dialogue: 0,2:57:06.41,2:57:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只不过对方忘了告诉别人\NThey just forgot to tell somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,2:57:08.00,2:57:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们杀错人了\NSo it was a bad hit.
Dialogue: 0,2:57:13.12,2:57:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米的儿子查奇  他的养子\NJimmy's son, Chuckie, you know, his foster son,
Dialogue: 0,2:57:15.33,2:57:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也参与了这件事\Nwas in the thing, too,
Dialogue: 0,2:57:16.83,2:57:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他并不知情\Nbut he didn't know it.
Dialogue: 0,2:57:19.29,2:57:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,查奇只知道他要接\NAll Chuckie knew was he was pickin' up
Dialogue: 0,2:57:21.41,2:57:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和一个普罗的人\None of Pro's guys and me,
Dialogue: 0,2:57:23.16,2:57:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们要一起到红狐餐厅\Nand we was all gonna pick up his dad
Dialogue: 0,2:57:25.29,2:57:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接他爸去开会\Nat the Red Fox for a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,2:57:27.91,2:57:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他参与了这件事  没错\NWell, I mean, he was in it, yeah,
Dialogue: 0,2:57:29.37,2:57:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以这么说  但他是糊里糊涂的\Nyou could say that, but stupidly.
Dialogue: 0,2:57:32.37,2:57:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直对查奇心怀愧疚\NI... I always felt sorry for Chuckie in this whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,2:57:35.20,2:57:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在仍然很愧疚\NAnd I... I still do.
Dialogue: 0,2:57:37.00,2:57:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,联调局因为一台车的破事\NAnd the Feds gave him ten months
Dialogue: 0,2:57:38.66,2:57:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让他被判刑十个月  事情大概就是这样\Nfor some bullshit thing about a car, and that's about it.
Dialogue: 0,2:57:41.33,2:57:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道是在搞什么\NWho knows what the fuck...
Dialogue: 0,2:57:44.70,2:57:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胖子托尼・萨雷诺因为所得税的事情被抓\NFat Tony Salerno, they got on an income tax thing.
Dialogue: 0,2:57:48.91,2:57:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不久之后\NA little while after,
Dialogue: 0,2:57:49.87,2:57:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他被查出患有前列腺癌\Nhe was diagnosed with prostate cancer.
Dialogue: 0,2:57:56.29,2:57:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,北加州有一家\NThere's a... a pork store up in...
Dialogue: 0,2:58:01.50,2:58:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,猪肉店\Nnorthern California.
Dialogue: 0,2:58:04.75,2:58:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在\NRight around...
Dialogue: 0,2:58:07.20,2:58:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,核桃溪市边上\NWalnut Creek.
Dialogue: 0,2:58:08.12,2:58:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是从那里来的  对吧\NYou're from up there, ain't you?
Dialogue: 0,2:58:10.08,2:58:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-对  -嗯\N- Yeah. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:58:11.62,2:58:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可能还认识店主\NAnd you might even know the guy that runs it.
Dialogue: 0,2:58:14.45,2:58:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实  我想让你帮个忙\NActually, I'm looking for a little favor...
Dialogue: 0,2:58:17.12,2:58:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮他  不是帮我\Nfor him, not for me.
Dialogue: 0,2:58:19.91,2:58:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能不能帮他弄张机票  比如去澳大利亚的\NBut if you can get him a ticket, like, to Australia...
Dialogue: 0,2:58:25.20,2:58:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你懂我的意思\NYou know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,2:58:29.04,2:58:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:58:31.62,2:58:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意帮他出国吗\NYou want to help him get down there?
Dialogue: 0,2:58:39.20,2:58:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愿意\NYe... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:58:40.41,2:58:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗素被抓了\NNow, Russell, he got pinched
Dialogue: 0,2:58:42.20,2:58:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为杰克・拿波里从他那赊账\Nfor telling Jimmy the Weasel to strangle Jack Napoli
Dialogue: 0,2:58:44.83,2:58:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿走了价值两万五的珠宝却没还钱\Nover some beef about 25 grand of jewelry
Dialogue: 0,2:58:47.62,2:58:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,于是他让黄鼠狼吉米\Nthat Jack took on credit from Russell
Dialogue: 0,2:58:50.16,2:58:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去把杰克勒死\Nand then he never paid for.
Dialogue: 0,2:58:52.33,2:58:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能对罗素做这样的事\NNow, with Russ, you don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,2:58:55.75,2:58:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问题在于  黄鼠狼叛变了\NSo, only thing is, the Weasel, he flipped.
Dialogue: 0,2:58:59.04,2:59:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他身上带了窃听器\NHe had a wire on him.
Dialogue: 0,2:59:00.91,2:59:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们声称他"密谋杀害目击者"\NThey called it "conspiracy to kill a witness."
Dialogue: 0,2:59:03.54,2:59:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,显而易见的是\NIt was obvious to everybody else
Dialogue: 0,2:59:04.83,2:59:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿波里做得不对\Nthat Napoli was clearly in the wrong.
Dialogue: 0,2:59:06.66,2:59:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这难道不明显吗\NI mean, how could you not see that?
Dialogue: 0,2:59:08.87,2:59:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他陷害了他  这是诱捕\NHe set him up. It was entrapment.
Dialogue: 0,2:59:10.75,2:59:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道不是吗\NWhat else could you call it?
Dialogue: 0,2:59:12.33,2:59:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这件事我现在也不想细说\NBut that's another thing I don't wanna get into now.
Dialogue: 0,2:59:16.62,2:59:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,举起右手\NRaise your right hand.
Dialogue: 0,2:59:17.41,2:59:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们把我送上法庭  指控我行贿和工会诈骗\NThey brought me up on bribery and labor racketeering charges
Dialogue: 0,2:59:20.79,2:59:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有其他一些我不知道的破事\Nand some other bullshit things I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,2:59:22.58,2:59:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谋杀  谋杀未遂  恐吓  挪用公款  纵火
Dialogue: 0,2:59:23.25,2:59:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是否向上帝发誓  你所说的全是事实\Nthe whole truth and nothing but the truth,
Dialogue: 0,2:59:25.08,2:59:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-没有任何隐瞒  -我发誓\N- so help you God? - I do.
Dialogue: 0,2:59:26.66,2:59:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是否还告诉他们巴法先生\NDid you also tell them that Mr. Boffa
Dialogue: 0,2:59:28.79,2:59:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送了你和你妻子豪车\Nhad given you and your wife luxury vehicles?
Dialogue: 0,2:59:30.91,2:59:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科尔先生  我工作了44年\NMr. Cole, I worked for 44 years,
Dialogue: 0,2:59:34.16,2:59:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没收过巴法或者别人的任何不法之财\NI never took one dime illegal off Boffa or nobody else.
Dialogue: 0,2:59:38.62,2:59:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么想是你的事  跟我没关系\NYou can think whatever you wanna think. Don't matter to me.
Dialogue: 0,2:59:41.08,2:59:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他们能落实的罪名  只有我炸了一家吊车公司\NBut all they got me for was blowing up a crane company
Dialogue: 0,2:59:44.16,2:59:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家公司开除了我的两个工会谈判代表\Nthat fired two of my shop stewards
Dialogue: 0,2:59:46.25,2:59:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却没有正当的理由\Nfor no good reason.
Dialogue: 0,2:59:49.91,2:59:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有我的林肯汽车\NAnd... And my Lincoln.
Dialogue: 0,2:59:52.37,2:59:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从尤金・巴法手里买下来的\NI mean, I bought that car from Eugene Boffa.
Dialogue: 0,2:59:55.87,2:59:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他向货运公司出租卡车司机\NHe leased truck drivers to freight companies,
Dialogue: 0,2:59:58.45,3:00:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后付给他们低于正常标准的工资\Nand then he paid them substandard wages.
Dialogue: 0,3:00:03.25,3:00:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们说我买这辆车花的钱\NThey said I paid a lot less for the car
Dialogue: 0,3:00:05.50,3:00:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,远低于其价值\Nthan what it was worth.
Dialogue: 0,3:00:07.58,3:00:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们说这辆车是贿赂\NThey said the car was a bribe.
Dialogue: 0,3:00:15.70,3:00:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱这辆车\NI... I... I loved that car.
Dialogue: 0,3:00:18.37,3:00:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但它不值得我为它坐十八年牢\NBut it wasn't worth the 18 years they gave me for it.
Dialogue: 0,3:00:22.37,3:00:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是肯定的\NThat's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,3:00:28.29,3:00:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗素中风了\NRussell, he had a stroke.
Dialogue: 0,3:00:30.70,3:00:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胖托尼尿失禁了\NFat Tony, he couldn't control his urine no more.
Dialogue: 0,3:00:34.29,3:00:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在安齐奥的散兵坑里得上的关节炎\NAnd my arthritis that started in the foxholes of Anzio
Dialogue: 0,3:00:38.91,3:00:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不断折磨着我的腰\Nwas eatin' away at my lower back now,
Dialogue: 0,3:00:41.54,3:00:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的脚已经没什么知觉了\Nand I couldn't feel much in my feet no more.
Dialogue: 0,3:00:44.58,3:00:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要拄拐杖\NI needed a cane.
Dialogue: 0,3:00:45.70,3:00:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他们不会在牢里给你配拐杖\NBut, you know, they're not gonna give you a cane in the can
Dialogue: 0,3:00:48.66,3:00:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们怕你把它当作武器\Nbecause they say you're gonna use it as a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,3:00:51.58,3:00:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一种叫诺立汀的药\NThere was this medicine, Neurontin,
Dialogue: 0,3:00:53.33,3:00:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我有点帮助\Nit helped me a little bit,
Dialogue: 0,3:00:54.50,3:00:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但也会使你神经错乱\Nbut it also made you loopy.
Dialogue: 0,3:00:56.62,3:00:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他要打中了\NHe's got it!
Dialogue: 0,3:00:58.20,3:00:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他要打中了\NHe's got it!
Dialogue: 0,3:01:00.79,3:01:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在严寒中\NWe were all falling apart right there
Dialogue: 0,3:01:02.12,3:01:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都要崩溃了\Nin the freezing fucking cold.
Dialogue: 0,3:01:03.79,3:01:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里就能看到  你现在怕了吗\NI can see it from here. You getting scared now?
Dialogue: 0,3:01:05.66,3:01:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你再练个十年\NYeah, you stay here another fucking ten years,
Dialogue: 0,3:01:07.58,3:01:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才有可能赢我\Nyou'll beat me.
Dialogue: 0,3:01:17.91,3:01:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是好喝的葡萄汁吗\NIs this the good grape juice?
Dialogue: 0,3:01:32.54,3:01:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我吃不了这个\NI can't eat it.
Dialogue: 0,3:01:34.41,3:01:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-吃一口  -我没牙  吃不了\N- Take a bite. - I got no teeth. I can't.
Dialogue: 0,3:01:36.12,3:01:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我一小块\NPut a little piece.
Dialogue: 0,3:01:37.91,3:01:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一小块就好  谢谢\NJust a little piece, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,3:01:39.33,3:01:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还要吗\NThat's it?
Dialogue: 0,3:01:53.87,3:01:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好吃吧  -好吃\N- E buono, no? - Buono.
Dialogue: 0,3:01:56.20,3:01:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃\NBuono.
Dialogue: 0,3:02:02.00,3:02:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米是个好人\NJimmy was a good man.
Dialogue: 0,3:02:04.20,3:02:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他还有美满的家庭  不是吗\NYou know? He had a nice family too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,3:02:09.58,3:02:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我知道\NYeah. Yeah. I know.
Dialogue: 0,3:02:13.04,3:02:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从没想过要把事情做这么绝\NI never wanted it to go that far.
Dialogue: 0,3:02:24.66,3:02:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我为了我们的利益而放弃了他\NI picked us over him.
Dialogue: 0,3:02:28.33,3:02:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去他们的\NFuck 'em.
Dialogue: 0,3:02:30.54,3:02:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去他们的\NFuck 'em.
Dialogue: 0,3:02:33.54,3:02:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去他们的\NFuck 'em.
Dialogue: 0,3:02:40.50,3:02:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧  小子  吃吧\NMangia che cresci... figlio mio, mangia.
Dialogue: 0,3:02:59.33,3:03:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗素\NHey, Russ.
Dialogue: 0,3:03:00.62,3:03:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗兰克\NHey, Frankie.
Dialogue: 0,3:03:01.91,3:03:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你要去哪  -什么\N- Where you goin'? - What?
Dialogue: 0,3:03:03.75,3:03:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你要去哪  -我要去教堂\N- Where you goin'? - I'm going to church.
Dialogue: 0,3:03:06.79,3:03:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教堂\NChurch?
Dialogue: 0,3:03:08.20,3:03:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别笑  到时你就知道了\NDon't laugh, you'll see.
Dialogue: 0,3:03:09.91,3:03:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别笑\NDon't laugh.
Dialogue: 0,3:03:11.62,3:03:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到时你就知道了\NYou'll see.
Dialogue: 0,3:03:20.70,3:03:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗素去了教堂\NRussell went to church.
Dialogue: 0,3:03:24.62,3:03:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后来他去了监狱的医院\NThen he went to the prison hospital.
Dialogue: 0,3:03:30.04,3:03:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再后来他进了坟墓\NAnd... And then he went to the graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,3:03:36.20,3:03:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主耶稣基督\NLord Jesus Christ...
Dialogue: 0,3:03:39.33,3:03:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在那年的十月出狱了\NI got out that October.
Dialogue: 0,3:03:41.25,3:03:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琳妮在十二月去世了\NReenie died in December.
Dialogue: 0,3:03:43.70,3:03:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准确地说是12月23日\NOn December 23rd, to be exact.
Dialogue: 0,3:03:46.83,3:03:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肺癌\NLung cancer.
Dialogue: 0,3:03:48.50,3:03:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一点也不意外\NNo surprise.
Dialogue: 0,3:03:50.66,3:03:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使夺去了我们必死的身躯\N...even as it claims our mortal bodies.
Dialogue: 0,3:03:53.83,3:03:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们的姐妹在此安眠\NGrant that our sister may sleep here in peace,
Dialogue: 0,3:03:56.70,3:03:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直至您用荣光将她唤醒\Nuntil you awaken her to glory.
Dialogue: 0,3:03:59.70,3:04:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为您就是复苏和生命\NFor you are the resurrection and the life.
Dialogue: 0,3:04:02.45,3:04:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后她将与您面对面\NAnd then she will see you face to face,
Dialogue: 0,3:04:05.08,3:04:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在您的光明中看见光明\Nand in your light will see light,
Dialogue: 0,3:04:07.58,3:04:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感受上帝的光辉  直到永远\Nand know the splendor of God for ever and ever.
Dialogue: 0,3:04:12.16,3:04:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿门\NAmen.
Dialogue: 0,3:04:46.16,3:04:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个赛季他的击打率比生涯平均的29.6%\N...six points shy of his career average of .296
Dialogue: 0,3:04:51.16,3:04:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,低了六个百分点\Ncoming into this season.
Dialogue: 0,3:04:52.79,3:04:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,费城队阵容里前四位击球员\NTop four batters in this lineup for Philadelphia
Dialogue: 0,3:04:55.58,3:04:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是左右手都能打的\Ntoday are all switch hitters.
Dialogue: 0,3:05:51.66,3:05:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使一些政策制定者失望的是\NMuch to the frustration of some policy makers,
Dialogue: 0,3:05:54.29,3:05:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,北约军事领导人不会冒险\NNATO military leaders will not risk
Dialogue: 0,3:05:57.12,3:06:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对科索沃的塞尔维亚军队发动低空袭击\Nlow flying attacks on Serb troops in Kosovo.
Dialogue: 0,3:06:01.95,3:06:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还需要进行多日的系统轰炸\NIt could take days more of systematic bombing,
Dialogue: 0,3:06:05.25,3:06:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是因为塞尔维亚人\Nespecially since the Serbs
Dialogue: 0,3:06:06.58,3:06:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将很多防空导弹藏了起来\Nhave hidden so many of their anti-aircraft missiles,
Dialogue: 0,3:06:09.75,3:06:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想引诱北约军队进行低空空袭\Nin essence, daring NATO to fly low.
Dialogue: 0,3:06:35.62,3:06:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去吧  去吧\NYou go... you go there. Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,3:06:38.37,3:06:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧\NYeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,3:06:45.95,3:06:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暂停营业\N请到隔壁柜台
Dialogue: 0,3:06:48.79,3:06:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佩琪\NPeggy.
Dialogue: 0,3:06:49.87,3:06:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佩琪  我只是想和你聊聊\NPeggy. I just want to talk.
Dialogue: 0,3:07:14.25,3:07:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是  我...\NI just, you know... I...
Dialogue: 0,3:07:16.20,3:07:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她走开了\NShe walked away.
Dialogue: 0,3:07:18.75,3:07:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道她生我的气  但我想...\NI know she's mad at me and all, but I... I want...
Dialogue: 0,3:07:21.45,3:07:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打给她  打给她  我只是想和她聊聊\NCall her. Call her. I just want to talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,3:07:25.66,3:07:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和她聊什么呢\NTalk to her and tell her what?
Dialogue: 0,3:07:27.83,3:07:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么\NWhat...
Dialogue: 0,3:07:29.29,3:07:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想跟她道个歉  仅此而已\NI just want to say I'm sorry. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,3:07:32.95,3:07:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么道歉\NFor?
Dialogue: 0,3:07:36.45,3:07:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着\NLook...
Dialogue: 0,3:07:38.66,3:07:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我不是个好父亲  我知道\NI know I wasn't a... a good dad. I know that.
Dialogue: 0,3:07:41.79,3:07:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  我只是想保护她\NI know that. I was just trying to protect her.
Dialogue: 0,3:07:44.50,3:07:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保护你们每个人不受伤害\NProtect all of youse.
Dialogue: 0,3:07:45.62,3:07:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我做的事\NI mean, that's what I was doing. That's...
Dialogue: 0,3:07:49.16,3:07:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受什么伤害\NFrom what?
Dialogue: 0,3:07:51.41,3:07:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切事情\NWell, everything.
Dialogue: 0,3:07:53.00,3:07:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说\NI mean...
Dialogue: 0,3:07:54.37,3:07:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,某种程度上  你们以前过着受保护的生活\NYou... Youse had a sheltered life, in a way,
Dialogue: 0,3:07:58.04,3:07:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们没见过我所见过的事\Nbecause you didn't see what I see
Dialogue: 0,3:07:59.91,3:08:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没经历过我所经历的事\Nand what I've been through.
Dialogue: 0,3:08:03.08,3:08:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外面有很多坏人\NThere's a lot of bad people out there.
Dialogue: 0,3:08:06.04,3:08:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还能做什么\NWhat else am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,3:08:08.33,3:08:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸  你根本不知道我们以前的感受\NDaddy, you have no idea what it was like for us.
Dialogue: 0,3:08:12.50,3:08:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们出了问题没法找你\NI mean, we couldn't go to you with a problem
Dialogue: 0,3:08:14.16,3:08:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怕你会做不好的事\N'cause of what you would do.
Dialogue: 0,3:08:15.75,3:08:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们没法向你寻求保护\NYou know, we couldn't come to you for protection
Dialogue: 0,3:08:18.16,3:08:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你会做可怕的事\Nbecause of the terrible things that you would do.
Dialogue: 0,3:08:23.37,3:08:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是  只是\NI was just... I was...
Dialogue: 0,3:08:24.37,3:08:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想看你们受到伤害  仅此而已\NI didn't want to see youse get hurt, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,3:08:32.00,3:08:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你们读到过  听说过很多我的事情\NI know you read a lot of things about me, heard about me.
Dialogue: 0,3:08:35.08,3:08:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,3:08:36.66,3:08:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...\NI...
Dialogue: 0,3:08:39.75,3:08:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在能做些什么来补偿你们吗\NCan I do anything now to make it up to you?
Dialogue: 0,3:08:54.66,3:08:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想要奢华一点的\NIf you're looking for something with a little bit more luxury,
Dialogue: 0,3:08:57.08,3:08:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有这两款\Nwe have these two models over here.
Dialogue: 0,3:08:59.29,3:09:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它们就像棺材界的凯迪拉克\NThey're like the Cadillacs of caskets.
Dialogue: 0,3:09:01.95,3:09:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你要火化的话\NNow, if we puttin' you in the fuckin' oven,
Dialogue: 0,3:09:03.58,3:09:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用什么棺材其实都无所谓\Nit really doesn't matter what you go in.
Dialogue: 0,3:09:05.87,3:09:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越便宜越好\NThe cheapest shit possible.
Dialogue: 0,3:09:07.45,3:09:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,复合板就够了\NParticle board, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,3:09:09.41,3:09:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后事打算怎么办  火葬吗\NWhat are we doin' today? Are we doin' a cremation?
Dialogue: 0,3:09:12.58,3:09:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-土葬  -土葬\N- A burial. - Burial?
Dialogue: 0,3:09:15.25,3:09:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是男人还是女人\NIs it for a man or for a woman?
Dialogue: 0,3:09:16.91,3:09:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我\NMe.
Dialogue: 0,3:09:18.95,3:09:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠\NShit.
Dialogue: 0,3:09:24.45,3:09:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有喜欢的吗\NYou see anything you like?
Dialogue: 0,3:09:37.16,3:09:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-那个绿色的  -那个很漂亮\N- That green one. - That's a beauty.
Dialogue: 0,3:09:39.29,3:09:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你今天就买的话\NThat one'll set you back about $7,500
Dialogue: 0,3:09:41.54,3:09:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概要七千五百块\Nif you take it home today.
Dialogue: 0,3:09:43.87,3:09:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得呢\NWhat do you think?
Dialogue: 0,3:09:46.37,3:09:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能便宜点吗\NCan you do any better?
Dialogue: 0,3:09:48.45,3:09:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伙计  你想在这棺材里长眠是吧\NI mean, buddy, this is what you want to go home in, no?
Dialogue: 0,3:09:54.75,3:09:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就算你六千吧  怎么样\NI think we could go six on that for you. How about that?
Dialogue: 0,3:09:57.95,3:10:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-六千现金  行吗  -可以\N- Six flat cash work for you? - That's good.
Dialogue: 0,3:10:01.45,3:10:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以\NGood for me.
Dialogue: 0,3:10:22.45,3:10:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迟早\NSooner or later,
Dialogue: 0,3:10:24.20,3:10:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这世上每一个人都有离开的那天\Neverybody put here has a date when he's gonna go.
Dialogue: 0,3:10:27.29,3:10:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人生就是如此\NThat's just the way it is.
Dialogue: 0,3:10:30.04,3:10:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为离开的时候肯定会发生什么\NAnd I think there's gotta be something when you go
Dialogue: 0,3:10:34.66,3:10:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然  这一切到底是怎么开始的\N'cause, I mean, how the hell did this whole thing start?
Dialogue: 0,3:10:43.00,3:10:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比我聪明的人都没搞清楚\NPeople smarter than me can't figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,3:10:45.50,3:10:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我绝对不会选择火葬\NThat's why I would never go for cremation
Dialogue: 0,3:10:47.33,3:10:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为那就真的结束了\Nbecause it's so... it's so final.
Dialogue: 0,3:10:51.58,3:10:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个\NThis... This one.
Dialogue: 0,3:10:54.50,3:10:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1948号\N1948.
Dialogue: 0,3:10:57.08,3:11:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对埋葬你的人来说最难接受的\NThat's the hardest part of anybody when they bury youse,
Dialogue: 0,3:11:00.12,3:11:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是入土的时候\Nis when they go into the ground
Dialogue: 0,3:11:02.00,3:11:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为那就真的结束了\Nbecause it's... it's so final.
Dialogue: 0,3:11:05.62,3:11:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你要埋在房子里  房子还在\NIf you go into a building, the building's there.
Dialogue: 0,3:11:08.08,3:11:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,墓还在\NThe crypt is there.
Dialogue: 0,3:11:09.58,3:11:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要用金属棺材\NIt has to be a metal casket,
Dialogue: 0,3:11:11.20,3:11:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们把你放在房间里\Nand they have you in the room.
Dialogue: 0,3:11:13.41,3:11:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都放好\NAnd all that there.
Dialogue: 0,3:11:14.87,3:11:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不算完全结束了\NIt's just not as final.
Dialogue: 0,3:11:16.16,3:11:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你死了  但还没结束\NYou're dead, but it ain't that final.
Dialogue: 0,3:11:22.29,3:11:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  如果你们想谈霍法先生的事\NI'm sorry, but I gotta direct youse to my attorney,
Dialogue: 0,3:11:26.54,3:11:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就得\NMr. Ragano...
Dialogue: 0,3:11:29.62,3:11:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你们去找我的律师\Nif youse want to talk about Mr. Hoffa or...
Dialogue: 0,3:11:32.75,3:11:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷加诺先生\Nor any matter, for that matter.
Dialogue: 0,3:11:34.83,3:11:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有别的可说的\NI got noth... nothing new to say.
Dialogue: 0,3:11:37.79,3:11:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他死了\NHe's dead.
Dialogue: 0,3:11:39.79,3:11:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁死了\NWho's dead?
Dialogue: 0,3:11:41.45,3:11:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的律师  雷加诺先生\NYour attorney, Mr. Ragano.
Dialogue: 0,3:11:43.00,3:11:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他死了  -是的\N- He's dead? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,3:11:43.87,3:11:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁干的\NWho did it?
Dialogue: 0,3:11:46.79,3:11:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,癌症\NCancer.
Dialogue: 0,3:11:50.58,3:11:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都死了  希兰先生\NEverybody's dead, Mr. Sheeran.
Dialogue: 0,3:11:54.29,3:11:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结束了\NIt's over.
Dialogue: 0,3:11:55.95,3:11:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们都死了\NThey're all gone.
Dialogue: 0,3:11:57.37,3:11:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗素  安吉洛  萨雷诺\NRussell, Angelo, Salerno,
Dialogue: 0,3:11:59.70,3:12:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,普罗  多夫曼  小虫萨利\NPro, Dorfman, Sally Bugs.
Dialogue: 0,3:12:02.04,3:12:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们都死了\NThey're gone.
Dialogue: 0,3:12:04.83,3:12:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在保护谁\NWho are you protecting?
Dialogue: 0,3:12:08.29,3:12:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道谁没死吗\NYou know who's not gone?
Dialogue: 0,3:12:11.20,3:12:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霍法先生的家人  他的孩子们\NMr. Hoffa's family. His children.
Dialogue: 0,3:12:14.08,3:12:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们还活着  他们一辈子都得不到真相\NThey're here. And they gotta live not knowing.
Dialogue: 0,3:12:18.54,3:12:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那很难熬\NThat's hard to do.
Dialogue: 0,3:12:22.66,3:12:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也有孩子  弗兰克\NI mean, you got kids, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,3:12:24.95,3:12:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能想象吗\NCan you imagine?
Dialogue: 0,3:12:31.70,3:12:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗兰克  是时候了  该说出真相了\NFrank, it's time. It's time you say what happened.
Dialogue: 0,3:12:41.70,3:12:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们看起来人不错\NYou seem like nice fellas.
Dialogue: 0,3:12:44.58,3:12:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你们亲自来找我\NI appreciate youse coming to see me.
Dialogue: 0,3:12:47.45,3:12:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我帮不了你们\NBut I... I can't help you.
Dialogue: 0,3:12:53.08,3:12:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样吗\NThat's it?
Dialogue: 0,3:12:53.95,3:12:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样\NThat's it.
Dialogue: 0,3:13:01.87,3:13:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圣母玛利亚\NHoly Mary, Mother of God...
Dialogue: 0,3:13:04.50,3:13:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圣母玛利亚\NHoly Mary, Mother of God...
Dialogue: 0,3:13:05.83,3:13:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-请为我们这些罪人祈祷  -请为我们这些罪人祈祷\N- Pray for us sinners... - Pray for us sinners...
Dialogue: 0,3:13:08.45,3:13:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-现在和我们临终时  -现在和我们临终时\N- Now and at the hour of our death. - Now and at the hour of our death.
Dialogue: 0,3:13:12.12,3:13:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-阿门  -阿门\N- Amen. - Amen.
Dialogue: 0,3:13:16.54,3:13:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这...\NThat was...
Dialogue: 0,3:13:18.25,3:13:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这还不错\NThat wasn't too bad.
Dialogue: 0,3:13:20.08,3:13:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很久没祷告过了\NIt's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,3:13:21.91,3:13:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很不错\NNot bad at all.
Dialogue: 0,3:13:23.00,3:13:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真心实意的  发自内心\NAnd the intention was there. The intention.
Dialogue: 0,3:13:25.41,3:13:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,3:13:27.20,3:13:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你是发自内心的\NI know the intention is there.
Dialogue: 0,3:13:29.16,3:13:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的  神父\NIt was there, Father.
Dialogue: 0,3:13:32.20,3:13:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你对自己做过的事\NDo you feel anything for...
Dialogue: 0,3:13:34.33,3:13:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有任何感觉吗\Nfor what you've done?
Dialogue: 0,3:13:40.08,3:13:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有  不过也许...\NI, I don't. I mean, maybe that...
Dialogue: 0,3:13:44.45,3:13:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在坐在这里跟你说话\NBecause I'm here now talking to you,
Dialogue: 0,3:13:46.37,3:13:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许这本身就是\Nthat in itself is,
Dialogue: 0,3:13:48.41,3:13:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一种尝试...\Nyou know, an attempt to...
Dialogue: 0,3:13:55.37,3:13:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你真的一点感觉都没有吗\NBut you don't feel anything at all?
Dialogue: 0,3:14:00.29,3:14:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,3:14:03.87,3:14:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是过去的事了\NWater under the dam.
Dialogue: 0,3:14:10.00,3:14:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对他的家人有没有愧疚呢\NAny... Any remorse for the families?
Dialogue: 0,3:14:14.33,3:14:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不认识他的家人\NI... I didn't know the families.
Dialogue: 0,3:14:19.75,3:14:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不认识他们  只认识一个\NI didn't know 'em. Except one I knew.
Dialogue: 0,3:14:27.58,3:14:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为我们可以悔过\NI think we can... we can be sorry...
Dialogue: 0,3:14:30.62,3:14:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以悔过  即使我们不觉得难过\NWe can be sorry even when we don't feel sorry.
Dialogue: 0,3:14:34.20,3:14:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以做出意志上的决定\NWell, for us to say, to make a decision of the will...
Dialogue: 0,3:14:37.20,3:14:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"上帝啊\N"God...
Dialogue: 0,3:14:38.87,3:14:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉  上帝\NI am sorry, God.
Dialogue: 0,3:14:42.25,3:14:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原谅我"\NForgive me."
Dialogue: 0,3:14:44.41,3:14:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是意志上的决定\NAnd that... that's a decision of the will.
Dialogue: 0,3:14:55.00,3:14:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么样的人\NWhat kind of man
Dialogue: 0,3:14:58.20,3:15:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会打那样一通电话\Nmakes a... a phone call like that?
Dialogue: 0,3:15:06.50,3:15:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思  什么电话\NWhat do you mean? What phone call?
Dialogue: 0,3:15:08.75,3:15:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能告诉你\NWell, I can't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,3:15:13.41,3:15:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能  我得...\NI can't. I got...
Dialogue: 0,3:15:15.87,3:15:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系\NThat's okay.
Dialogue: 0,3:15:20.50,3:15:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗兰克  你想再和我祷告一次吗\NFrank, do you wanna pray with me again?
Dialogue: 0,3:15:22.41,3:15:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,3:15:24.33,3:15:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次我们用自己的话来说  好吗\NThis time, we'll do it in our own words. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,3:15:26.29,3:15:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,3:15:29.45,3:15:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝啊  我们来到您面前\NGod, we come before you
Dialogue: 0,3:15:32.16,3:15:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罪孽深重  忧伤不已\Nsinful and sorrowful.
Dialogue: 0,3:15:34.75,3:15:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罪孽深重  忧伤不已\NSinful and sorrowful.
Dialogue: 0,3:15:38.08,3:15:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们知道您善良仁慈\NWe know you are all good and all merciful.
Dialogue: 0,3:15:42.25,3:15:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们知道您善良仁慈\NWe know you are all good and all merciful.
Dialogue: 0,3:15:46.75,3:15:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我们请求您  -我们请求您\N- We ask you... - We ask you...
Dialogue: 0,3:15:49.83,3:15:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用您的眼光\Nto help us see ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,3:15:52.04,3:15:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用您的眼光\Nto help us see ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,3:15:55.04,3:15:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-帮我们看清自己  -帮我们看清自己\N- as you see us. - as you see us.
Dialogue: 0,3:16:00.70,3:16:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我女儿  佩琪\NThat's my daughter, Peggy.
Dialogue: 0,3:16:02.70,3:16:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是吗  -是的\N- Is it? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,3:16:04.25,3:16:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好像还没见过她\NI don't think I've met her yet.
Dialogue: 0,3:16:05.83,3:16:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不怎么过来\NWell, she... she ain't been around too much.
Dialogue: 0,3:16:08.91,3:16:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是你的独生女吗\NIs she your only child?
Dialogue: 0,3:16:10.54,3:16:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我有四个女儿\NNo, I got four daughters.
Dialogue: 0,3:16:12.87,3:16:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看\NOver there. See?
Dialogue: 0,3:16:14.66,3:16:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮\NBeautiful.
Dialogue: 0,3:16:16.37,3:16:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-大忙人  -是啊\N- Busy man. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,3:16:19.95,3:16:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,3:16:22.08,3:16:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她身旁是谁\NWho's that with her?
Dialogue: 0,3:16:24.83,3:16:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道这是谁\NYou don't know who that is?
Dialogue: 0,3:16:28.29,3:16:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,3:16:30.29,3:16:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米・霍法\NJimmy Hoffa.
Dialogue: 0,3:16:33.62,3:16:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他啊\NOh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,3:16:34.37,3:16:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得了吧  "是他啊"\NYeah, right, "Oh, yeah."
Dialogue: 0,3:16:37.87,3:16:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道他是谁\NYou don't know who he is.
Dialogue: 0,3:16:39.45,3:16:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  我不知道\NOkay, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,3:16:41.91,3:16:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  你想不到时间过得有多快\NYeah. Boy, you don't know how fast time goes by
Dialogue: 0,3:16:44.95,3:16:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了已经晚了\Nuntil you get there.
Dialogue: 0,3:16:47.25,3:16:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过你不用担心这个\NBut you don't have to worry about that
Dialogue: 0,3:16:48.95,3:16:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你还有大把的好时光\Nbecause you have your whole life ahead of you.
Dialogue: 0,3:16:51.75,3:16:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长得很  时间过得太快...\NForever. It goes fast, time...
Dialogue: 0,3:16:54.58,3:16:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说\NI'm tellin' ya.
Dialogue: 0,3:16:55.79,3:16:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在给你量脉搏  希兰先生\NI'm trying to take your pulse, Mr. Sheeran.
Dialogue: 0,3:16:57.54,3:16:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请不要说话\NPlease, please don't talk.
Dialogue: 0,3:17:01.16,3:17:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天很不错\NIt's great today.
Dialogue: 0,3:17:03.04,3:17:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还活着\NI'm still alive?
Dialogue: 0,3:17:04.25,3:17:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是的  -真是好消息\N- Yes, you are. - That's good to know.
Dialogue: 0,3:17:07.08,3:17:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活得好好的\NAlive and well.
Dialogue: 0,3:17:08.50,3:17:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在没事了\NAnd you're free
Dialogue: 0,3:17:09.95,3:17:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过晚些时候还要再给你检查一遍\Ntill later today when we have to put you through all this again.
Dialogue: 0,3:17:12.45,3:17:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我哪都不去\NI'm here.
Dialogue: 0,3:17:32.58,3:17:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...教会之奉\N...ministry of the church.
Dialogue: 0,3:17:34.20,3:17:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愿上帝赐予你宽恕与平静  弗兰克\NMay God grant you pardon and peace, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,3:17:37.25,3:17:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我赦免你的罪\NAnd I absolve you from your sins.
Dialogue: 0,3:17:38.45,3:17:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以圣父  圣子\NIn the name of the Father, and of the Son,
Dialogue: 0,3:17:40.95,3:17:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圣灵的名义  阿门\Nand of the Holy Spirit, amen.
Dialogue: 0,3:17:44.12,3:17:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感谢上帝  因为上帝仁慈\NGive thanks to the Lord, for he is good.
Dialogue: 0,3:17:46.95,3:17:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的慈爱\NHis mercy...
Dialogue: 0,3:17:48.04,3:17:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他的慈爱永远长存  -永远长存\N- His mercy endures forever. - endures forever.
Dialogue: 0,3:17:50.66,3:17:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  弗兰克  我很快就会再来看你\NAll right, Frank. I'll be back to visit, okay? Very soon.
Dialogue: 0,3:17:53.66,3:17:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概圣诞假期后\NProbably after the Christmas holidays.
Dialogue: 0,3:17:57.08,3:17:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,3:17:58.00,3:18:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-弗兰克  上帝保佑你  -你也是  谢谢\N- Frank, God bless you. - You too. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,3:18:03.04,3:18:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞节到了\NIt's Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,3:18:05.29,3:18:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快了\NAlmost.
Dialogue: 0,3:18:07.37,3:18:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我哪也不去\NWell, I ain't going nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,3:18:11.70,3:18:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-神父  -怎么\N- Father? - Yup?
Dialogue: 0,3:18:14.37,3:18:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮我个忙好吗\NDo me a favor?
Dialogue: 0,3:18:16.16,3:18:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别把门关严  我不喜欢那样\NDon't shut the door all the way. I don't like that. Just...
